#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: title
#: content/community/_index.md:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Community"
msgstr "Fællesskab"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/community/_index.md:7
#, no-wrap
msgid "Whether it be to solve a problem or to contribute in any way, the Xfce communities are a good place to get help or to share your ideas. You might also want to have a look at the communities of the different distributions which provide Xfce.\n"
msgstr "Hvad enten det er at løse et problem eller at bidrage på nogen måde, så er Xfce-fællesskabet et godt sted at få hjælpe eller dele dine ideer. Du vil måske også være interesseret i kigge på fællesskaberne for de forskellige distributioner som leverer Xfce.\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/community/_index.md:8
#, no-wrap
msgid "Mailing lists"
msgstr "Mailinglister"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/community/_index.md:11
#, no-wrap
msgid "Almost all development and coordination work is taking place on the Xfce mailing lists. A summary of all lists is available at [mail.xfce.org](https://mail.xfce.org). There is also a user-specific list where you can ask questions and freely discuss about the desktop.\n"
msgstr "Næsten al udvikling og koordineringsarbejde finder sted på Xfce's mailinglister. En oversigt over alle lister findes på [mail.xfce.org](https://mail.xfce.org). Der er også en bruger-specifik liste, hvor du kan stille spørgsmål og frit diskutere skrivebordet.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/community/_index.md:13
#, no-wrap
msgid "**NOTE:** In order to post to these lists, you must first subscribe.\n"
msgstr "**BEMÆRK**: for at kunne skrive til disse lister, skal du første abonnere.\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/community/_index.md:14
#, no-wrap
msgid "Matrix"
msgstr "Matrix"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/community/_index.md:17
#, no-wrap
msgid "If you have a problem that you cannot resolve, you might want to try asking a question in our Matrix channel [#xfce](https://matrix.to/#/#xfce:matrix.org). The channel has several active users. It is recommended that you consult the [documentation](https://docs.xfce.org/) about your problem before asking your question.\n"
msgstr "Hvis du har et problem som ikke kan løses, så kan du prøve at spørge i vores Matrix-kanal [#xfce](https://web.libera.chat/#xfce). Kanalen har flere aktive brugere. Det anbefales at du konsulterer [dokumentationen](https://docs.xfce.org/) om dit problem inden du spørger.\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/community/_index.md:18
#, no-wrap
msgid "Forums"
msgstr "Fora"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/community/_index.md:21
#, no-wrap
msgid "For users who prefer forums, the [Xfce Forum](https://forum.xfce.org/) is the place to be. Active contributors will be able to help you, but please do not use it for bug reports.\n"
msgstr "Til brugere som foretrækker fora findes [Xfce-foraet](https://forum.xfce.org/). Aktive bidragsydere vil være i stand til at hjælpe dig, men brug det venligst ikke til fejlrapporter.\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/community/_index.md:22
#, no-wrap
msgid "Social Networks"
msgstr "Sociale netværk"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/community/_index.md:24
#, no-wrap
msgid "You can follow us on the official [Mastodon account](https://floss.social/@xfce) or [Twitter account](https://twitter.com/xfceofficial)\n"
msgstr "Du kan følge os på vores officielle [Mastodon-konto](https://floss.social/@xfce) eller [Twitter-konto](https://twitter.com/xfceofficial)\n"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: title
#: content/about/_index.md:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "About"
msgstr "Om"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/_index.md:7
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce is a lightweight desktop environment for UNIX-like operating systems. It aims to be fast and low on system resources, while still being visually appealing and user friendly.\n"
msgstr "Xfce er et letvægtsskrivebordsmiljø til UNIX-lignende styresystemer. Det bestræber sig på at være hurtigt og bruge få systemressourcer, mens det stadig er visuelt indbydende og brugervenligt.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/_index.md:9
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce embodies the traditional UNIX philosophy of modularity and re-usability. It consists of a number of components that provide the full functionality one can expect of a modern desktop environment. They are packaged separately and you can pick among the available packages to create the optimal personal working environment.\n"
msgstr "Xfce følger den traditionelle UNIX-filosofi om at være modulær og genbrugelig. Det består af et antal komponenter, som giver den fulde funktionalitet, som man kan forvente af et moderne skrivebordsmiljø. De er pakket separat, og du kan vælge mellem de tilgængelige pakker for at skabe det optimale personlige arbejdsmiljø.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/_index.md:11
#, no-wrap
msgid "Another priority of Xfce is adherence to standards, specifically those defined at [freedesktop.org](https://freedesktop.org).\n"
msgstr "En anden af Xfce's prioriteter er at overholde standarder, specielt dem der er defineret på [freedesktop.org](https://freedesktop.org).\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/_index.md:13
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce can be installed on several UNIX platforms. It is known to compile on Linux, NetBSD, FreeBSD, OpenBSD, Solaris, Cygwin and MacOS X, on x86, PPC, Sparc, Alpha...\n"
msgstr "Xfce kan installeres på adskillige UNIX-platformer. Det er kendt at den kan kompilere på Linux, NetBSD, FreeBSD, OpenBSD, Solaris, Cygwin og MacOS X, på x86, PPC, Sparc, Alpha ...\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/_index.md:14
#, no-wrap
msgid "Features"
msgstr "Funktionaliteter"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/_index.md:17
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce contains a number of core components for the minimum tasks you'd expect from a desktop environment:\n"
msgstr "Xfce indeholder et antal kernekomponenter til de grundlæggende opgaver, du forventer fra et skrivebordsmiljø:\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/_index.md:18 content/about/tour44.md:49
#, no-wrap
msgid "Window Manager"
msgstr "Vindueshåndtering"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/_index.md:21
#, no-wrap
msgid "Manages the placement of windows on the screen, provides window decorations and manages workspaces or virtual desktops.\n"
msgstr "Håndterer placeringen af vinduer på skærmen, giver vinduesdekorationer og håndterer arbejdsområder eller virtuelle skriveborde.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/_index.md:22
#, no-wrap
msgid "Desktop Manager"
msgstr "Skrivebordshåndtering"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/_index.md:25
#, no-wrap
msgid "Sets the background image and provides a root window menu, desktop icons or minimized icons and a windows list.\n"
msgstr "Sætter baggrundsbilledet og giver en root-vinduesmenu, skrivebordsikoner eller minimeret ikoner og en vinduesliste.\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/_index.md:26 content/about/tour44.md:69
#, no-wrap
msgid "Panel"
msgstr "Panel"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/_index.md:29
#, no-wrap
msgid "Switch between opened windows, launch applications, switch workspaces and menu plugins to browse applications or directories.\n"
msgstr "Skift mellem åbne vinduer, start programmer, skift arbejdsområder og menu-plugins til at gennemse programmer eller mapper.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/_index.md:30
#, no-wrap
msgid "Session Manager"
msgstr "Sessionshåndtering"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/_index.md:33
#, no-wrap
msgid "Controls the login and power management of the desktop and allows you to store multiple login sessions.\n"
msgstr "Styrer skrivebordets login og strømstyring, og giver dig mulighed for at gemme flere login-sessioner.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/_index.md:34
#, no-wrap
msgid "Application Finder"
msgstr "Programfinder"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/_index.md:37
#, no-wrap
msgid "Shows the applications installed on your system in categories, so you can quickly find and launch them.\n"
msgstr "Viser de programmer som er installeret på dit system, i kategorier, så du hurtigt kan finde og starte dem.\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/_index.md:38 content/about/tour44.md:21
#, no-wrap
msgid "File Manager"
msgstr "Filhåndtering"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/_index.md:41
#, no-wrap
msgid "Provides the basic file-management features and unique utilities like the bulk renamer.\n"
msgstr "Giver grundlæggende funktionaliteter til håndtering af filer og unikke redskaber såsom masseomdøbning af filer.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/_index.md:42 content/about/tour410.md:69
#, no-wrap
msgid "Settings Manager"
msgstr "Indstillingshåndtering"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/_index.md:45
#, no-wrap
msgid "Tools to control the various settings of the desktop; like keyboard shortcuts, appearance, display settings, etc.\n"
msgstr "Værktøjer til at styre skrivebordets forskellige indstillinger såsom tastaturgenveje, udseende, skærmindstillinger osv.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/_index.md:46
#, no-wrap
msgid "Beside the basic set of modules, Xfce also provides numerous additional applications and plugins so you can extend your desktop the way you like, for example a terminal emulator, text editor, sound mixer, application finder, image viewer, iCal based calendar and a CD and DVD burning application. You can read more about the modules of Xfce in the [projects](/projects) page.\n"
msgstr "Udover de basale sæt af moduler leverer Xfce også utallige yderligere programmer og plugins, så du kan udvide dit skrivebord på den måde, du kan lide, f.eks. en terminalemulator, tekstredigeringsprogram, lyd-mikser, programfinder, billedfremviser, iCal-baseret kalender og et cd- og dvd-brændingsprogram. Du kan læse mere om modulerne i Xfce på [projekter](/projects)-siden.\n"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: title
#: content/getinvolved/_index.md:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Get Involved"
msgstr "Deltag"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/getinvolved/_index.md:7
#, no-wrap
msgid "Welcome to the Xfce community. By joining our team, you will be part of an international effort by hundreds of people working to deliver a stunning Free Software computing experience. You will meet new friends, learn new skills and make a difference to millions of users while working with people from all around the globe. There are many different ways you can become part of this, just read on and pick an area which interests you or seems challenging.\n"
msgstr "Velkommen til Xfce-fællesskabet. Ved at deltage på vores hold, så bliver du en del af en international indsats, bestående af hundredvis af individer, der arbejder for at levere en bragende computeroplevelse med fri software. Du vil møde nye venner, lære nye færdigheder og gøre en forskel for millioner af brugere, mens du arbejder med folk fra hele verden. Der er mange forskellige måder at blive en del af dette - læs blot videre og udvælg et område, der interesserer eller ser ud til at udfordre dig.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/getinvolved/_index.md:9
#, no-wrap
msgid "Possible tasks include testing, bug reporting; writing code, developing artwork, documentation or translations; or spreading the word and helping out with promotion and marketing both on line and at tradeshows and conferences.\n"
msgstr "Mulige opgaver inkluderer test, fejlrapportering, skrivning af kode, udvikling af grafik, dokumentation eller oversættelser; eller hjælpe med at dele budskabet og hjælpe med at promovere og markedsføre både online, samt ved handelsmesser og konferencer.\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/getinvolved/_index.md:10
#, no-wrap
msgid "Documentation"
msgstr "Dokumentation"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/getinvolved/_index.md:13
#, no-wrap
msgid "There's lots of people using and testing Xfce. By providing useful and up-to-date documentation, you will make a big impact on helping people understand how to make the most of the Xfce Desktop Environment. [Learn More →](https://docs.xfce.org/contribute/documentation)\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ##
#: content/getinvolved/_index.md:14
#, no-wrap
msgid "Translation"
msgstr "Oversættelse"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/getinvolved/_index.md:17
#, no-wrap
msgid "Are you fluent in multiple languages? By contributing your translations of text to the Xfce Desktop Environment, you will help Xfce be a better part of the global market and more accessible to the millions of potential users out there. [Learn More →](https://docs.xfce.org/contribute/translate/start)\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ##
#: content/getinvolved/_index.md:18
#, no-wrap
msgid "Development"
msgstr "Udvikling"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/getinvolved/_index.md:21
#, no-wrap
msgid "By becoming a developer, you can make a big difference while enjoying a challenging and fun experience. You'll learn to be a better coder, you will get to implement new features and defeat daunting bugs, creating a stunning product, all the while collaborating with people from all around the world. You can start by browsing the [source code](https://gitlab.xfce.org).\n"
msgstr "Ved at blive en udvikler kan du gøre en stor forskel, mens du får glæde af udfordrende og sjove oplevelser. Du lærer at blive en dygtigere koder, du får mulighed for at implementere nye funktionaliteter og overkomme krævende fejl, skabe et fremragende produkt - alt sammen gennem samarbejde med mennesker fra hele verden. Du kan starte med at gennemse [kildekoden](https://gitlab.xfce.org).\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/getinvolved/_index.md:22
#, no-wrap
msgid "Promotion"
msgstr "Promovering"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/getinvolved/_index.md:25
#, no-wrap
msgid "If you own a blog or website you can greatly help by spreading the word and encouraging new users to give Xfce a try. If you have a Mastodon or Twitter account you can also help by reposting any announcements we make to help us reach a larger audience.\n"
msgstr "Hvis du har en blog eller websted kan du hjælpe meget ved at sprede budskabet og opfordre nye brugere til at prøve Xfce. Hvis du har en Mastodon- eller Twitter-konto kan du også hjælpe ved at genposte de bekendtgørelser vi laver, for at hjælpe med at nå et større publikum.\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/getinvolved/_index.md:26
#, no-wrap
msgid "Bug Reporting and testing"
msgstr "Fejlrapportering og test"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/getinvolved/_index.md:29
#, no-wrap
msgid "One of the most useful tasks that we rely on the community for is testing and reporting of bugs. Since Xfce runs on various platform and in a lot of different setups, testing all changes in every possible situation is an impossible task. As such we kindly ask users to assist in testing, and reporting all bugs they may find, using our [bug tracker](https://gitlab.xfce.org).\n"
msgstr "En af de mest nyttige opgaver som vi beror på fællesskabet er testning og rapportering af fejl. Eftersom Xfce kører på adskillige platforme og på mange forskellige opsætninger, er det en umulig opgave at teste ændringer i alle tænkelige situationer. I og for sig anmoder vi venligst vores brugere om at assistere med testning og rapportering af alle fejl de måtte finde, ved at bruge vores [bug tracker](https://gitlab.xfce.org).\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/getinvolved/_index.md:31
#, no-wrap
msgid "Once a bug has been found, the cause of the bug needs to be tracked down, and then (obviously) fixed. If you want to get involved in the actual development process of Xfce a great way to start is by solving bugs and then submitting a patch file.\n"
msgstr "Når en fejl er fundet, skal årsagen til fejlen findes og så (selvfølgelig) rettes. Hvis du vil deltage i selve udviklingsprocessen af Xfce, er en god måde at begynde, at løse fejl og så indsende en patch-fil.\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/getinvolved/_index.md:32
#, no-wrap
msgid "OpenCollective"
msgstr "OpenCollective"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/getinvolved/_index.md:34
#, no-wrap
msgid "If you want to fund the project, you can use OpenCollective. Xfce has created two collectives, known as [Xfce ($)](https://opencollective.com/xfce) and [Xfce-Eu (€)](https://opencollective.com/xfce-eu) respectively. [Learn More →](https://mail.xfce.org/pipermail/xfce/2021-May/037348.html)\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: title
#: content/about/tour420.md:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce 4.20 tour"
msgstr "Xfce 4.20 rundvisning"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:8
#, no-wrap
msgid "This tour will introduce you to new major features of Xfce 4.20. It only covers improvements made on the (user-visible) surface.\n"
msgstr "Denne rundvisning introducerer dig for nye større funktionaliteter i Xfce 4.20. Den dækker kun forbedringer som er lavet på overfladen (det som brugeren kan se).\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:10
#, no-wrap
msgid "Check the full [Xfce 4.20 changelog](/download/changelogs/4.20/) for a detailed list of changes.\n"
msgstr "Tjek den komplette [Xfce 4.20 ændringslog](/download/changelogs/4.20/) for en detaljeret liste med ændringer.\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour420.md:11 content/about/tour420.md:204
#: content/about/tour418.md:223
#, no-wrap
msgid "General"
msgstr "Generelt"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:13
#, no-wrap
msgid "Wayland"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:16
#, no-wrap
msgid "**Important Notice:** Please be aware that the Wayland support in Xfce 4.20 is experimental. It is recommended for advanced users only, as you may encounter bugs and experience incomplete functionality. Proceed with caution!\n"
msgstr "<b>Vigtig bemærkning:</b> Vær venligst opmærksom på at understøttelse af Wayland i Xfce 4.20 er eksperimental. Det anbefales kun til avancerede brugere, så det kan være du støder på fejl og oplever funktionalitet der ikke virker fuldtud. Fortsæt med forsigtighed!\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:18
#, no-wrap
msgid "Thanks to [Brian](https://gitlab.xfce.org/kelnos) and [Gaël](https://gitlab.xfce.org/Tamaranch) almost all Xfce components are able to run on Wayland windowing, while still keeping support for X11 windowing.\n"
msgstr "Takket være [Brian](https://gitlab.xfce.org/kelnos) og [Gaël](https://gitlab.xfce.org/Tamaranch) kan næsten alle Xfce-komponenter køre på Wayland-windowing, mens understøttelse af X11-windowing er bevaret.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:20
#, no-wrap
msgid "This major effort was achieved by abstracting away any X11/Wayland windowing specific calls and making use of Wayland/Wlroots protocols. A whole new Xfce library, \"libxfce4windowing\" was introduced during that process. XWayland will not be required to run any of the ported Xfce components.\n"
msgstr "Det store arbejde blev opnået ved at gå væk fra X11-/Wayland-windowing specifikke kald og bruge Wayland-/Wlroots-protokoller. I forløbet blev det helt nye Xfce-bibliotek \"libxfce4windowing\" introduceret. Det er ikke nødvendigt at bruge XWayland for at køre de porterede Xfce-komponenter.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:22
#, no-wrap
msgid "So far Xfce does not feature a compositor which supports Wayland. If you want to run Xfce in Wayland, Labwc and Wayfire will give you the best results. A detailed instruction on this can be found [here](https://wiki.xfce.org/releng/wayland_roadmap#testing). Please be aware that Wayland support is still experimental!\n"
msgstr "Indtil videre har Xfce ikke en kompositør der understøtter Wayland. Hvis du vil køre Xfce i Wayland, så giver Labwc og Wayfire de bedste resultater. Du kan finde detaljeret instruktioner om det [her](https://wiki.xfce.org/releng/wayland_roadmap#testing). Vær venligst opmærksom på at understøttelse af Wayland er eksperimental!\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:24
#, no-wrap
msgid "Plans are underway to add Wayland support to Xfwm4 while preserving its existing X11 functionality. However, such a restructurization will be a major effort and we cannot tell yet when/if it will be done, so please don't hold your breath waiting for it.\n"
msgstr "Der er planer om at tilføje understøttelse af Wayland til Xfwm4 samtidig med at den eksisterende X11-funktionalitet bevares. Men sådan en omstrukturering kræver meget arbejde og vi kan endnu ikke sige hvornår/om det vil ske, så vent venligst ikke på at det kommer til at ske snart.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:26
#, no-wrap
msgid "For few components and multiple features, it was not possible to port them to Wayland, partly because there are no standardized Wayland protocols available yet to provide the required services:\n"
msgstr "Nogle få komponenter og adskillige funktioner kunne ikke porteres til Wayland, delvist pga. at der endnu ikke findes nogen standardiserede Wayland-protokoller til at levere de nødvendige tjenester:\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/tour420.md:32
#, no-wrap
msgid "Workspace support is missing (ext-workspace protocol [was just merged](https://gitlab.freedesktop.org/wayland/wayland-protocols/-/merge_requests/40)).\n"
msgstr "Understøttelse af arbejdsområder mangler (protokollen ext-workspace [er netop blevet sammenlagt](https://gitlab.freedesktop.org/wayland/wayland-protocols/-/merge_requests/40)).\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/tour420.md:32
#, no-wrap
msgid "Systray icons will be missing for multiple applications (required to use StatusNotifier instead of GtkStatusIcon)\n"
msgstr "Systembakkeikoner mangler for adskillige programmer (det er nødvendigt at bruge StatusNotifier i stedet for GtkStatusIcon)\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/tour420.md:32
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce4-settings: Keyboard and mouse settings so far are internal to the Wayland compositor and as such the according Xfce dialogs won't be available on Wayland yet.\n"
msgstr "Xfce4-settings: Tastatur- og museindstillinger er indtil videre interne i Wayland-kompositøren og de tilhørende Xfce-dialoger vil endnu ikke være tilgængelige i Wayland.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/tour420.md:32
#, no-wrap
msgid "Power related keyboard handling (brightness keys, suspend, etc.) is internal to the Wayland compositor and as such cannot be supported yet by Xfce components.\n"
msgstr "Strømrelaterede tastaturhandling (knapper til lysstyrke, hvile osv.) er interne i Wayland-kompositøren og kan endnu ikke understøttes af Xfce-komponenter.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/tour420.md:32
#, no-wrap
msgid "Wayland does not specify a native protocol for taking screenshots. However, xfce4-screenshooter already supports screenshots via the wlroots 'screencopy' protocol (entire screen). Screenshots of a rectangle selection or the active window are not yet supported via Wayland.\n"
msgstr "Wayland har ikke nogen indbygget protokol til at tage skærmbilleder. xfce4-screenshooter understøtter dog allerede skærmbilleder via wlroots's 'screencopy'-protokol (hele skærmen). Skærmbilleder af et firkantet område som vælges eller det aktive vindue understøttes endnu ikke via Wayland.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:34
#, no-wrap
msgid "Some other Xfce components don't run at all on Wayland:\n"
msgstr "Andre Xfce-komponenter som slet ikke kører på Wayland:\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/tour420.md:40
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfwm4\n"
msgstr "Xfwm4\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/tour420.md:40
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfdashboard\n"
msgstr "Xfdashboard\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/tour420.md:40
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce4-screensaver (porting to Wayland [completed but not merged](https://gitlab.xfce.org/apps/xfce4-screensaver/-/merge_requests/28), as it requires the experimental [libwlembed library](https://gitlab.xfce.org/kelnos/libwlembed))\n"
msgstr "Xfce4-screensaver (portering til Wayland er [færdig men ikke sammenlagt](https://gitlab.xfce.org/apps/xfce4-screensaver/-/merge_requests/28), eftersom det kræver det eksperimentale [libwlembed-bibliotek](https://gitlab.xfce.org/kelnos/libwlembed))\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/tour420.md:40
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce4-windowck-plugin (needs to be [ported to libxfce4windowing](https://gitlab.xfce.org/panel-plugins/xfce4-windowck-plugin/-/issues/37))\n"
msgstr "Xfce4-windowck-plugin (skal [porteres til libxfce4windowing](https://gitlab.xfce.org/panel-plugins/xfce4-windowck-plugin/-/issues/37))\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/tour420.md:40
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce4-xkb-plugin (keyboard handling is internal to the Wayland compositor)\n"
msgstr "Xfce4-xkb-plugin (tastaturhandling er intern i Wayland-kompositøren)\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:42
#, no-wrap
msgid "More detailed info on the current Wayland status can be found on our [Wayland roadmap.](https://wiki.xfce.org/releng/wayland_roadmap)\n"
msgstr "Mere detaljeret information om den nuværende status for Wayland kan findes i vores [Wayland roadmap.](https://wiki.xfce.org/releng/wayland_roadmap)\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:43 content/about/tour418.md:225
#, no-wrap
msgid "Scaling"
msgstr "Skalering"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:46
#, no-wrap
msgid "Icons and thumbnail scaling was fixed for various components. Various missing icons for larger scales were added. Any blurriness when using Xfce components on a HiDPI display should be gone now.\n"
msgstr "Skalering af ikoner og miniaturer blev rettet for diverse komponenter. Diverse ikoner som manglende til større skaleringer blev tilføjet. Den uskarphed der måtte være ved brug at Xfce-komponenter på en HiDPI-skærm burde være væk nu.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:49
#, no-wrap
msgid "Icon View Performance"
msgstr "Ydelse ved visning af ikoner"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:52
#, no-wrap
msgid "By using different container types, the \"Exo-Icon-View\" now can handle 100,000 files and more without freezing.\n"
msgstr "Ved at bruge andre beholdertyper kan \"Exo-Icon-View\" nu håndtere 100.000 filer, og mere, uden at fryse.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:53
#, no-wrap
msgid "Type ahead search box"
msgstr "Søgeboks med forudskrivning"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:56
#, no-wrap
msgid "The type ahead search box in the exo icon view now always stays inside the according view widget.\n"
msgstr "Søgeboksen med forudskrivning i exo's ikonvisning bliver nu altid inden i visning-widgeten.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:59
#, no-wrap
msgid "Shortcut Editor"
msgstr "Genvejsredigering"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:62
#, no-wrap
msgid "Shortcuts now can be used for multiple actions if they don't conflict with each other.\n"
msgstr "Genveje kan nu bruge til mere end én handling hvis ikke de er i konflikt med hinanden.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:63
#, no-wrap
msgid "About Dialog"
msgstr "Dialogen Om"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:66
#, no-wrap
msgid "The dialog now shows the distribution logo, information about the used windowing system and the used GPU.\n"
msgstr "Dialogen viser nu distributionens logo, information om windowingsystemet og GPU'en.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:68
#, no-wrap
msgid "![libxfce4ui - about dialog][img-libxfce4ui_about]\n"
msgstr "![libxfce4ui - dialogen Om][img-libxfce4ui_about]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:72
#, no-wrap
msgid "This library is new to Xfce. Libxfce4windowing is an abstraction library that attempts to present windowing concepts (screens, top level windows, workspaces, etc.) in a windowing-system-independent manner.\n"
msgstr "Biblioteket er nyt i Xfce. Libxfce4windowing er et abstraktionsbibliotek der forsøger at vise windowing-koncepter (skærme, topniveau-vinduer, arbejdsområder osv.) på en måde der er uafhængig af et windowingsystem.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:74
#, no-wrap
msgid "Currently, X11 is fully supported via libwnck. Wayland is partially supported by using various Wayland protocol extensions. However, the full range of operations available on X11 is not available on Wayland, due to missing features in these protocols extensions.\n"
msgstr "På nuværende tidspunkt understøttes X11 fuldtud via libwnck. Wayland understøttes delvist brug af diverse Wayland-protokoludvidelser. Dog er hele det udvalg af handlinger der er tilgængelige i X11 ikke tilgængelige i Wayland, pga. manglende funktioner i disse protokoludvidelser.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:77
#, no-wrap
msgid "Mounted and Remote Locations"
msgstr "Monterede og fjernplaceringer"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:80
#, no-wrap
msgid "Mount points now show an emblem and have a specific type description.\n"
msgstr "Monteringspunkter viser nu et emblem og har en bestemt typebeskrivelse.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:82
#, no-wrap
msgid "Ipv6 remote URLs are now supported.\n"
msgstr "Ipv6 fjern-URL'er understøttes nu.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:84
#, no-wrap
msgid "It is now possible to create symbolic links as well on remote locations.\n"
msgstr "Det er nu muligt at oprette symbolske henvisninger på fjernplaceringer.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:85
#, no-wrap
msgid "Search"
msgstr "Søgning"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:88
#, no-wrap
msgid "It is not required any more to wait until a search is finished to open the context menu on search results.\n"
msgstr "Det er ikke længere nødvendigt at vente på at en søgning er færdig for at kunne  åbne genvejsmenuen i søgeresultater.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:89 content/about/tour418.md:107
#, no-wrap
msgid "Toolbar"
msgstr "Værktøjslinje"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:92
#, no-wrap
msgid "A couple of new toolbar buttons were added:\n"
msgstr "Der blev tilføjet nogle nye knapper på værktøjslinjen:\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/tour420.md:97
#, no-wrap
msgid "View Switcher - A drop-down button to select a view.\n"
msgstr "Visningsskifter - En nedrulningsmenu til at vælge en visning.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/tour420.md:97
#, no-wrap
msgid "Menu - This hamburger button will show automatically in the toolbar, when the menubar is hidden. It will reveal a vertical menu, bar, when pressed.\n"
msgstr "Menu - Hamburgerknappen vises automatisk i værktøjslinjen når menulinjen er skjult. Den viser en lodret menu, når der trykkes på den.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/tour420.md:97
#, no-wrap
msgid "New Tab - Open a new tab using the current directory.\n"
msgstr "Nyt faneblad - Åbn den nuværende mappe i et nyt faneblad.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/tour420.md:97
#, no-wrap
msgid "New Window - Open a new window using the current directory.\n"
msgstr "Nyt vindue - Åbn den nuværende mappe i et nyt vindue.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:99
#, no-wrap
msgid "![thunar - new toolbar buttons][img-thunar_toolbar_new_items]\n"
msgstr "![thunar - nye knapper på værktøjslinjen][img-thunar_toolbar_new_items]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:101
#, no-wrap
msgid "![thunar - improved hamburger toolbar button][img-thunar_toolbar_hamburger]\n"
msgstr "![thunar - forbedret hamburgerknap på værktøjslinjen][img-thunar_toolbar_hamburger]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:103
#, no-wrap
msgid "On shrinking the Thunar window, toolbar items will now be moved to an overflow menu. Like that, it is possible to maintain smaller thunar windows.\n"
msgstr "Når Thunar-vinduet gøres mindre flyttes værktøjslinjeelementer til en overløbsmenu. På den måde er det muligt at bruge mindre Thunar-vinduer.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:105
#, no-wrap
msgid "Furthermore, a bug was fixed which prevented the usage of submenu custom actions in the toolbar.\n"
msgstr "Derudover blev en fejl rettet som forhindrede brugen af tilpassede handlinger i undermenuer på værktøjslinjen.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:106
#, no-wrap
msgid "Window Decorations"
msgstr "Vinduesdekorationer"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:109
#, no-wrap
msgid "There is now an option to use client side decorations in Thunar (CSD).\n"
msgstr "Der er nu en valgmulighed til at bruge klientside-dekorationer i Thunar (CSD).\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:111
#, no-wrap
msgid "![thunar - CSD with menu][img-thunar_csd_with_menu]\n"
msgstr "![thunar - klientside-dekorationer med menu][img-thunar_csd_with_menu]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:113
#, no-wrap
msgid "![thunar - CSD without menu][img-thunar_csd_without_menu]\n"
msgstr "![thunar - klientside-dekorationer uden menu][img-thunar_csd_without_menu]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:114 content/about/tour418.md:127
#, no-wrap
msgid "Statusbar"
msgstr "Statuslinje"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:117
#, no-wrap
msgid "An option to show the number of hidden files in the statusbar was added.\n"
msgstr "Der blev tilføjet en valgmulighed til at vise antallet af skjulte filer i statuslinjen.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:118
#, no-wrap
msgid "Recently Used Files"
msgstr "Seneste brugte filer"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:121
#, no-wrap
msgid "Only files which were successfully opened are now added to the list of recently used files.\n"
msgstr "Nu er det kun filer som det lykkedes at åbne, der bliver tilføjet til listen over seneste brugte filer.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:123
#, no-wrap
msgid "Directories won't be added to the recently used files anymore.\n"
msgstr "Mapper tilføjes ikke længere til seneste brugte filer.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:124
#, no-wrap
msgid "Symbolic Icons"
msgstr "Symbolske ikoner"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:127
#, no-wrap
msgid "There is now an option to use symbolic icons in the side pane and colored icons in the toolbar.\n"
msgstr "Der er nu en valgmulighed til at bruge symbolske ikoner i sidepanelet og farvede ikoner på værktøjslinjen.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:129
#, no-wrap
msgid "![thunar - symbolic icons][img-thunar_symbolic_icons]\n"
msgstr "![thunar - symbolske ikoner][img-thunar_symbolic_icons]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:131
#, no-wrap
msgid "![thunar - colored icons][img-thunar_colored_icons]\n"
msgstr "![thunar - farvede ikoner][img-thunar_colored_icons]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:132
#, no-wrap
msgid "Drag and Drop"
msgstr "Træk og slip"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:135
#, no-wrap
msgid "While dragging files, folders are now opened automatically on hover.\n"
msgstr "Mapper åbnes nu automatisk når der trækkes filer henover.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:137
#, no-wrap
msgid "While dragging files, the focus of the split view pane is now updated when hovered.\n"
msgstr "Fokussen i ruden opdelt visning opdateres nu når der trækkes filer henover.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:138
#, no-wrap
msgid "Performance"
msgstr "Ydelse"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:141
#, no-wrap
msgid "In the past, you might have faced situation involving bigger numbers of files in which thunar showed a freeze. Due to various different performance measures, thunar now is much more bullet-proof for action involving huge numbers of files.\n"
msgstr "Før i tiden har du måske oplevet situationer hvor et stort antal filer fik Thunar til at fryse. Pga. diverse ydelsestiltag er Thunar nu meget mere skudsikker når der udføres handlinger med et stort antal filer.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:143
#, no-wrap
msgid "This was achieved by using appropriate container types, moving some actions into separate jobs and throttling of view-updates.\n"
msgstr "Det blev opnået ved at bruge beholdertyper som er egnet til formålet, flytte nogle handlinger ind i separate jobs og regulering af view-updates.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:145
#, no-wrap
msgid "A [number of integration test cases](https://wiki.xfce.org/thunar/dev/integration_testcases) will be used in order to keep performance on the current level in the future.\n"
msgstr "En [række integreringstestforsøg](https://wiki.xfce.org/thunar/dev/integration_testcases) vil blive brugt for at holde ydelsen på det nuværende niveau i fremtiden.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:146 content/about/tour418.md:171
#, no-wrap
msgid "Custom Actions"
msgstr "Tilpasset handlinger"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:149
#, no-wrap
msgid "Shortcuts for custom action will now as well work when the custom action is located in a sub-menu.\n"
msgstr "Genveje for tilpasset handling virker nu også når den tilpasset handling er placeret i en undermenu.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:150
#, no-wrap
msgid "File Transfer"
msgstr "Filoverførsel"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:153
#, no-wrap
msgid "For file validation in thunar 4.18.x a md5 checksum was calculated for source and target file. This calculation turned out to be rather slow and actually superfluous. Now files are just compared directly. In addition, the usage of direct I/O operations now attempts to prevent comparison of possibly cached buffers.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:155
#, no-wrap
msgid "An option was added to only copy files in parallel if the relevant devices are in idle state. This prevents possible fragmentation during copy for HDD drives.\n"
msgstr "Der blev tilføjet en valgmulighed til kun at kopiere i parallel hvis de relevante enheder er i inaktiv tilstand. Det forhindrer mulig fragmentering under kopiering på harddisk-drev.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:157
#, no-wrap
msgid "Transferring files no longer steals the current focus.\n"
msgstr "Overførsel af filer stjæler ikke længere den nuværende fokus.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:159
#, no-wrap
msgid "The file transfer question dialog now provides the same options while having less buttons. In addition, file thumbnails now are properly requested by the dialog.\n"
msgstr "Dialogen med spørgsmål om filoverførsel har nu de samme valgmuligheder med færre knapper. Derudover anmoder dialogen nu korrekt om filminiaturer.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:161
#, no-wrap
msgid "![thunar - file transfer dialog][img-thunar_transfer_dialog]\n"
msgstr "![thunar - dialog til filoverførsel][img-thunar_transfer_dialog]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:162
#, no-wrap
msgid "Launchers"
msgstr "Opstartere"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:165
#, no-wrap
msgid "By default, launcher names instead of filenames are shown now for trusted launchers.\n"
msgstr "For betroede opstartere vises nu som standard navne på opstartere, i stedet for filnavne.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:166
#, no-wrap
msgid "Undo/Redo"
msgstr "Fortryd/omgør"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:169
#, no-wrap
msgid "The user now will be asked before any deletion will be done by an undo operation.\n"
msgstr "Brugeren bliver nu spurgt før det udføres sletning af en fortryd-handling.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:170 content/about/tour418.md:73
#, no-wrap
msgid "List View"
msgstr "Listevisning"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:173
#, no-wrap
msgid "Similar to the tree-view side pane, the main view now also supports folder expansion.\n"
msgstr "Ligesom sidepanelets trævisning, understøtter hovedvisningen nu også udfoldning af mapper.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:175
#, no-wrap
msgid "![thunar - expandable folders][img-thunar_expandable_folders]\n"
msgstr "![thunar - mapper som kan foldes ud][img-thunar_expandable_folders]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:176 content/about/tour418.md:121
#, no-wrap
msgid "Split View"
msgstr "Opdelt visning"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:179
#, no-wrap
msgid "A shortcut now can be used to toggle between split-view panes, and the focused pane now uses different coloring.\n"
msgstr "Der kan nu bruges en genvej til at skifte mellem ruder med opdelt visning, og ruden med fokus har nu andre farver.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:181
#, no-wrap
msgid "![thunar - split view][img-thunar_split_view]\n"
msgstr "![thunar - opdelt visning][img-thunar_split_view]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:183
#, no-wrap
msgid "A dialog will now ask for confirmation when closing a split-pane with multiple tabs.\n"
msgstr "En dialog spørger nu om bekræftelse ved lukning af en opdelt rude med mere end ét faneblad.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:187
#, no-wrap
msgid "The application list now as well can be navigated via Ctrl+N / Ctrl+P keys (VI default).\n"
msgstr "Programlisten kan nu også navigeres via tasterne Ctrl+N / Ctrl+P (standard i VI).\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:189
#, no-wrap
msgid "An option was added to close the Appfinder window automatically when focus is lost.\n"
msgstr "Der blev tilføjet en valgmulighed til automatisk at lukke Appfinder-vinduet når der mistes fokus.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:191
#, no-wrap
msgid "Ctrl+Enter can be used to execute commands immediately when selecting entries from the dropdown.\n"
msgstr "Ctrl+Enter kan bruges til at udføre kommandoer med det samme når der vælges punkter i nedrulningen.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:193
#, no-wrap
msgid "Within the new version, application specific actions will show on right click.\n"
msgstr "I den nye version vises programspecifikke handlinger ved højreklik.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:195
#, no-wrap
msgid "An option to show generic names of launchers was added.\n"
msgstr "Der blev tilføjet en valgmulighed til at vise generiske navne på opstartere.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:197
#, no-wrap
msgid "Appfinder optionally can now be launched as a daemon, so that it will respond even quicker.\n"
msgstr "Appfinder kan nu valgfrit startes som en dæmon, så den reagerer endnu hurtigere.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:199
#, no-wrap
msgid "An option allows now to launch items on a single click.\n"
msgstr "En valgmulighed gør det nu muligt at starte elementer med ét enkelt klik.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:201
#, no-wrap
msgid "![xfce4-appfinder - settings][img-appfinder_new]\n"
msgstr "![xfce4-appfinder - indstillinger][img-appfinder_new]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:207
#, no-wrap
msgid "The border width of the panel is now configurable.\n"
msgstr "Bredden på kanten af panelet kan nu konfigureres.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:209
#, no-wrap
msgid "For manual installations: the panel now does its best to find plugins in XDG base directories, and better preserves its configuration when it can't find them.\n"
msgstr "For manuelle installationer: panelet gør nu sit bedste for at finde plugins i XDG-grundmapper, og bedre bevare sin konfiguration når det ikke kan finde dem.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:210
#, no-wrap
msgid "Clock"
msgstr "Ur"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:213
#, no-wrap
msgid "LCD clock: An option was added to visualize inactive segments.\n"
msgstr "LCD-ur: Der blev tilføjet en valgmulighed til at visualisere inaktive segmenter.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:215
#, no-wrap
msgid "Analog: There is now an optional 24h mode.\n"
msgstr "Analog: Der er nu en valgfri 24t-tilstand.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:217
#, no-wrap
msgid "Digital: Week numbers now are shown optionally.\n"
msgstr "Digital: Ugenumre vises nu valgfrit.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:218
#, no-wrap
msgid "Show Desktop"
msgstr "Vis skrivebord"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:221
#, no-wrap
msgid "There is now the possibility to show the desktop when hovering the mouse on the \"show desktop\" panel icon.\n"
msgstr "Det er nu muligt at vise skrivebordet når musen holdes over panelikonet \"vis skrivebord\".\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:222
#, no-wrap
msgid "Tasklist"
msgstr "Opgaveliste"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:225
#, no-wrap
msgid "Icon size management has been improved overall, notably by switching to libxfce4windowing.\n"
msgstr "Håndtering af ikonstørrelse er generelt blevet forbedret, især ved at skifte til libxfce4windowing.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:226 content/about/tour420.md:354
#: content/about/tour418.md:179
#, no-wrap
msgid "Preferences"
msgstr "Præferencer"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:229
#, no-wrap
msgid "The 'delete' key can now be used to remove panel objects, and several objects can be removed at once.\n"
msgstr "'Slet'-knappen kan nu bruges til at fjerne panelobjekter og mere end ét objekt kan fjernes på samme tid.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:231
#, no-wrap
msgid "Panel objects in the panel configuration list now will have the same icons as in the panel itself.\n"
msgstr "Panelobjekter i panelkonfigurationslisten har nu de samme ikoner som i selve panelet.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:233
#, no-wrap
msgid "![xfce4-panel - panel configuration list][img-panel_item_list]\n"
msgstr "![xfce4-panel - panelkonfigurationsliste][img-panel_item_list]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:236
#, no-wrap
msgid "Screen Locking"
msgstr "Skærmlåsning"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:239
#, no-wrap
msgid "There is no dedicated \"security\" tab anymore. Lock screen management was massively simplified and \"Light Locker\" was dropped. \"lock-on-sleep\" is now synchronized with xfce4-session and xfce4-screensaver.\n"
msgstr "Der er ikke længere noget faneblad kaldet \"sikkerhed\". Håndtering af låseskærmen blev  meget mere enkel og \"Light Locker\" blev droppet. \"lock-on-sleep\" er nu synkroniseret med xfce4-session og xfce4-screensaver.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:241
#, no-wrap
msgid "Screen locking settings are now only handled by xfce4-screensaver to avoid conflicts. A button to open xfce4-screensaver-preferences was added:\n"
msgstr "Indstillinger for skærmlåsning håndteres nu kun af xfce4-screensaver for at forhindre konflikter. Der blev tilføjet en knap til at åbne xfce4-screensaver-preferences:\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:243
#, no-wrap
msgid "![xfce4-power-manager - settings][img-power_manager_settings]\n"
msgstr "![xfce4-power-manager - indstillinger][img-power_manager_settings]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:245
#, no-wrap
msgid "![xfce4-screensaver - settings][img-power_manager_screensaver]\n"
msgstr "![xfce4-screensaver - indstillinger][img-power_manager_screensaver]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:246
#, no-wrap
msgid "Power Settings"
msgstr "Strømindstillinger"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:249
#, no-wrap
msgid "Support for handling different power profiles via power-profiles-daemon was added.\n"
msgstr "Der blev tilføjet understøttelse til håndtering af forskellige strømprofiler via power-profiles-daemon.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:251
#, no-wrap
msgid "The overall charge state calculation was wrong for some cases and is now fixed.\n"
msgstr "Udregningen af den samlede opladningstilstand var i nogle tilfælde forkert og er nu rettet.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:253
#, no-wrap
msgid "When the critical power dialog pops up, unintentional user actions are now prevented.\n"
msgstr "Utilsigtede brugerhandlinger undgås nu, når dialogen kritisk strøm popper op.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:255
#, no-wrap
msgid "There is now support for the hybrid sleep mode.\n"
msgstr "Der er nu understøttelse af tilstanden hybrid søvn.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:257
#, no-wrap
msgid "The device details tab now as well shows the energy rate.\n"
msgstr "Fanebladet for enhedens detaljer viser nu også energiraten.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:258
#, no-wrap
msgid "Others"
msgstr "Andre"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:261
#, no-wrap
msgid "Several use-cases for lid close were fixed.\n"
msgstr "Flere anvendelsessituationer af lukning af låg blev rettet.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:263
#, no-wrap
msgid "There are now the options \"shutdown\" and \"do nothing\" on lid close.\n"
msgstr "Ved lukning af låg findes nu valgmulighederne \"luk ned\" og \"gør ingenting\".\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:265
#, no-wrap
msgid "Buttons to change the brightness exponentially and keyboard backlight toggle keys now are supported.\n"
msgstr "Der er nu understøttelse af knapper til at ændre lysstyrken eksponentielt og til at tænde/slukke for tastaturets baggrundsbelysning.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:269
#, no-wrap
msgid "The logout dialog will not provide a checkbox to enable session saving anymore.\n"
msgstr "Dialogen til udlogning har ikke længere nogen afkrydsningsboks til at gemme sessionen.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:271
#, no-wrap
msgid "It is now possible to start a Wayland session via `startxfce4 --wayland`.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:273
#, no-wrap
msgid "Minimal support for xdg-desktop-portal was added by registering for a wallpaper, screenshot and background xapp.\n"
msgstr "Der blev tilføjet minimal understøttelse af xdg-desktop-portal, ved at registrere efter et tapet-, skærmbillede- og baggrund-xapp.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:276 content/about/tour418.md:65
#: content/about/tour412.md:73 content/about/tour410.md:95
#, no-wrap
msgid "Appearance Settings"
msgstr "Udseendeindstillinger"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:279
#, no-wrap
msgid "Icon themes are now loaded in a separate thread, in order to prevent a possible freeze.\n"
msgstr "Ikontemaer indlæses nu i en separat tråd, for at undgå risikoen for en frysning.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:281
#, no-wrap
msgid "For icon themes which are known to be incomplete, a warning now will be shown.\n"
msgstr "Der vises nu en advarsel for ikontemaer der er kendt for ikke at være komplette.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:283
#, no-wrap
msgid "The usage of client side decorations is opt-in now, not opt-out.\n"
msgstr "Anvendelsen af klientside-dekorationer tilvælges nu, ikke fravælges.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:285
#, no-wrap
msgid "Dark themes now are identified and supported in a more reliable way. (Relevant e.g. for the Qogir and Orchis themes)\n"
msgstr "Mørke temaer identificeres og understøttes nu på en mere pålidelig måde (relevant for eksempelvis temaerne Qogir og Orchis)\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:286 content/about/tour418.md:59
#: content/about/tour412.md:65
#, no-wrap
msgid "Display Settings"
msgstr "Skærmindstillinger"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:289
#, no-wrap
msgid "The default display profile has been added to the list of profiles that can match, and will be used if more than one matches now.\n"
msgstr "Standardskærmprofilen er blevet tilføjet til listen over profiler som passer, og bruges nu hvis der er mere end ét resultat.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:291
#, no-wrap
msgid "Profile management has been extended to all profiles, not just those that match, and their names can now be edited.\n"
msgstr "Profilhåndtering er blevet udvidet til alle profiler, ikke bare dem der passer. Og deres navne kan nu redigeres.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:293
#, no-wrap
msgid "Scaling now always is done for both dimensions, and the preview shows the resulting size.\n"
msgstr "Skalering sker nu altid i begge retninger, og forhåndsvisningen viser størrelsen på resultatet.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:295
#, no-wrap
msgid "Mirror state management has been improved overall, in particular by removing the need to match refresh rates.\n"
msgstr "Håndtering af spejltilstand er generelt blevet forbedret, især fordi det ikke er nødvendigt at bruge den samme opdateringshastighed.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:297
#, no-wrap
msgid "The minimal dialog has been improved, in particular by allowing the display to be extended to the left and from top to bottom, and with compact profile display.\n"
msgstr "Den minimale dialog er blevet forbedret, især fordi skærmen kan udvides til venstre og fra øverst til nederst, og med kompakt profilvisning.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:299
#, no-wrap
msgid "![xfce4-settings - minimal display][img-settings_display]\n"
msgstr "![xfce4-settings - minimal visning][img-settings_display]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:300
#, no-wrap
msgid "Mouse Settings"
msgstr "Museindstillinger"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:303
#, no-wrap
msgid "A checkbox was added to toggle between adaptive and flat mouse accel profile.\n"
msgstr "En afkrydsningsboks blev tilføjet så man kan skifte mellem adaptiv og flad profil til acceleration af musen.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:305
#, no-wrap
msgid "High resolution scrolling can now be enabled for mice which do support it.\n"
msgstr "Rulning i høj opløsning kan nu aktiveres for mus der understøtter det.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:307
#, no-wrap
msgid "![xfce4-settings - mouse][img-settings_mouse]\n"
msgstr "![xfce4-settings - mus][img-settings_mouse]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:308
#, no-wrap
msgid "Mime Settings"
msgstr "MIME-indstillinger"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:311
#, no-wrap
msgid "It is now possible to select/change multiple items at once.\n"
msgstr "Det er nu muligt at vælge/ændre flere elementer på samme tid.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:315
#, no-wrap
msgid "A systemd user unit, corresponding to the D-Bus session service, is now added.\n"
msgstr "Der er tilføjet en systemd-brugerenhed, der tilsvarer D-Bus-sessiontjenesten.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:317
#, no-wrap
msgid "Whitespaces are now properly escaped when writing a xfconf channel to disk.\n"
msgstr "Blanktegn undviges nu korrekt når en xfconf-kanal skrives til disk.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:319
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfconf-query now displays array contents.\n"
msgstr "Xfconf-query viser nu indholdet i et gitter.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:322
#, no-wrap
msgid "Background Management"
msgstr "Baggrundshåndtering"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:325
#, no-wrap
msgid "For random wallpaper cycling, wallpapers now are only repeated after all other wallpapers were shown.\n"
msgstr "Til tilfældig visning af tapeter gentages tapet nu kun efter alle andre tapeter er blevet vist.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:327
#, no-wrap
msgid "Old Xfce backgrounds were ported from .png to .svg to be usable for large screens.\n"
msgstr "Gamle Xfce-baggrunde blev overført fra .png til .svg, så de kan bruges på store skærme.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:329
#, no-wrap
msgid "Gradients will now be rendered in a gamma-correct way.\n"
msgstr "Farveovergange gengives nu på en måde der er korrekt for gamma.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:330
#, no-wrap
msgid "Icon grid"
msgstr "Ikongitter"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:333
#, no-wrap
msgid "The confirmation dialog for arranging desktop icons now is optional.\n"
msgstr "Beskæftigelsesdialogen til at opstille skrivebordsikoner er nu valgfri.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:335
#, no-wrap
msgid "It is now possible to set custom colors for icon labels and icon background.\n"
msgstr "Det er nu muligt at indstille tilpassede farver for ikoners etiketter og baggrund.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:337
#, no-wrap
msgid "The icon grid on each monitor is now independent of one another.\n"
msgstr "Ikongitteret på hver skærm fungerer nu uafhængigt af hinanden.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:338
#, no-wrap
msgid "Minimized Application Icons"
msgstr "Minimerede programikoner"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:341
#, no-wrap
msgid "Window icons are now initially shown on the monitor where the window was present before being minimized.\n"
msgstr "Vinduesikoner vises nu på den skærm hvor vinduet var før det blev minimeret.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:343
#, no-wrap
msgid "The context menu (when clicking on an empty space) now has more useful options than before.\n"
msgstr "Genvejsmenuen (når der klikkes på et tomt område) har nu flere nyttige valgmuligheder end før.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:344
#, no-wrap
msgid "File Icons"
msgstr "Filikoner"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:347
#, no-wrap
msgid "There is now an option to sort folders before files.\n"
msgstr "Der er nu en valgmulighed til at sortere mapper før filer.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:349
#, no-wrap
msgid "The positions of the icons are now saved in a way that should avoid icons moving around in unexpected ways when monitors are added and removed.\n"
msgstr "Placeringen af ikonerne gemmes nu på en måde som bør forhindre at ikonerne flyttes rundt på en uventet måde når skærme tilføjes og fjernes.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:351
#, no-wrap
msgid "New files and dropped files now will be placed near the current cursor location.\n"
msgstr "Nye filer og filer som slippes placeres nu nær den nuværende markørposition.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:353
#, no-wrap
msgid "Icons of fixed disks and drives can now be optionally shown.\n"
msgstr "Ikoner for faste diske og drev kan nu valgfrit blive vist.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:357
#, no-wrap
msgid "The 'Desktop Icons' tab was fully reworked.\n"
msgstr "Fanebladet 'Skrivebordsikoner' blev lavet helt om.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:359
#, no-wrap
msgid "![xfdesktop - settings - desktop icons][img-xfdesktop_settings_icons]\n"
msgstr "![xfdesktop - indstillinger - skrivebordsikoner][img-xfdesktop_settings_icons]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:361
#, no-wrap
msgid "All shortcuts of Xfdesktop now can be configured, using the XfceShortcutsManagers widget.\n"
msgstr "Alle genveje i Xfdesktop kan nu konfigureres med XfceShortcutsManagers-widgeten.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:363
#, no-wrap
msgid "![xfdesktop - settings - keyboard shortcuts][img-xfdesktop_settings_shortcuts]\n"
msgstr "![xfdesktop - indstillinger - tastaturgenveje][img-xfdesktop_settings_shortcuts]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:365
#, no-wrap
msgid "More folders that hold background images were added as shortcuts in the settings dialog.\n"
msgstr "Der blev tilføjet flere mapper med baggrundsbilleder som genveje i dialogen med indstillinger.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:367
#, no-wrap
msgid "The settings dialog will update if the background is changed from outside the dialog.\n"
msgstr "Indstillingsdialogen opdateres hvis baggrunden ændres udenfor dialogen.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:369
#, no-wrap
msgid "Wallpaper image folders now are loaded fully asynchronously to prevent lag.\n"
msgstr "Tapetbilledmapper indlæses nu fuldt asynkront for at forhindre forsinkelse.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:370
#, no-wrap
msgid "Context Menu"
msgstr "Genvejsmenu"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:373
#, no-wrap
msgid "Cascading custom actions will now as well shown correctly in Xfdesktop.\n"
msgstr "Tilpassede handlinger der foldes ud vises nu også korrekt i Xfdesktop.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:375
#, no-wrap
msgid "It is now possible to open multiple selected folders at once.\n"
msgstr "Det er nu muligt at åbne mere end én valgt mappe på samme tid.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:377
#, no-wrap
msgid "The context menu now opens on button press rather than button release, as most users will expect.\n"
msgstr "Genvejsmenuen åbnes nu når knappen trykkes ned fremfor når knappen slippes, som de fleste brugere forventer.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:379
#, no-wrap
msgid "The middle-click window list menu has new styling and added features.\n"
msgstr "Vindueslistemenuen for midterklik har et nyt udseende og tilføjede funktioner.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:383
#, no-wrap
msgid "Support for stretch theme variants\n"
msgstr "Understøttelse af strakte temavarianter\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:385
#, no-wrap
msgid "Compositor: Block softpipe for GLX vsync\n"
msgstr "Kompositør: Bloker softpipe for GLX vsync\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:387
#, no-wrap
msgid "Focus: Include skip taskbar/pager when passing focus\n"
msgstr "Fokus: Inkluder udelad fra opgavelinje/arbejdsområdeskifter når der gives fokus\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:389
#, no-wrap
msgid "Fix crash when alt-tabbing ([#762](https://gitlab.xfce.org/xfce/xfwm4/-/issues/762))\n"
msgstr "Ret nedbrud når alt-tab bruges ([#762](https://gitlab.xfce.org/xfce/xfwm4/-/issues/762))\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:391
#, no-wrap
msgid "<p align=\"right\"><small>Used theme: \"Greybird-dark\". Used icon-theme: \"elementary Xfce dark\".</small></p>\n"
msgstr "<p align=\"right\"><small>Anvendt tema: \"Greybird-dark\". Anvendt ikontema: \"elementary Xfce dark\".</small></p>\n"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: title
#: content/about/tour418.md:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce 4.18 tour"
msgstr "Xfce 4.18 rundvisning"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:8
#, no-wrap
msgid "This tour will introduce you to new major features of Xfce 4.18. It only covers improvements made on the (user-visible) surface.\n"
msgstr "Denne rundvisning introducerer dig for nye større funktionaliteter i Xfce 4.18. Den dækker kun forbedringer som er lavet på overfladen (det som brugeren kan se).\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:10
#, no-wrap
msgid "Check the full [Xfce 4.18 changelog](/download/changelogs/4.18/) for a detailed list of changes.\n"
msgstr "Tjek den komplette [Xfce 4.18 ændringslog](/download/changelogs/4.18/) for en detaljeret liste med ændringer.\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour418.md:11
#, no-wrap
msgid "Widget Library *(libxfce4ui)*"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour418.md:13
#, no-wrap
msgid "Filename Input Dialog"
msgstr "Dialog til indtastning af filnavne"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:16
#, no-wrap
msgid "XfceFilenameInput is a comfortable widget for filename input, which was added in order to prevent invalid filenames at an early stage and to give detailed feedback on the concrete problem.\n"
msgstr "XfceFilenameInput er en nem og bekvem widget til indtastning af filnavne, som blev tilføjet for at forhindre ugyldige filnavne på et tidligt stadie og for at give tilbagemelding om det konkrete problem.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:18
#, no-wrap
msgid "![XfceFilenameInput - trailing whitespaces][img-xfce4ui-new-file-dialog1]\n"
msgstr "![XfceFilenameInput - efterstillede blanktegn][img-xfce4ui-new-file-dialog1]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:20
#, no-wrap
msgid "![XfceFilenameInput - slash][img-xfce4ui-new-file-dialog2]\n"
msgstr "![XfceFilenameInput - skråstreg][img-xfce4ui-new-file-dialog2]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour418.md:21
#, no-wrap
msgid "Generic Shortcut Editor"
msgstr "Generisk genvejsredigering"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:24
#, no-wrap
msgid "This widget is a shortcut editor which was introduced in order to have a graphical interface to modify component-specific shortcuts. Currently, it is only used inside Thunar, Xfce4-terminal and Mousepad, though other components might follow.\n"
msgstr "Widgeten er en genvejsredigering som blev indført for at have en grafisk brugerflade til at ændre komponentspecifikke genveje. Den bruges i øjeblikket kun i Thunar, Xfce4-terminal og Mousepad, men andre komponenter kan følge.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:26
#, no-wrap
msgid "![XfceShortcutsEditor in Thunar][img-xfce4ui-shortcuts-editor]\n"
msgstr "![XfceShortcutsEditor i Thunar][img-xfce4ui-shortcuts-editor]\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour418.md:27
#, no-wrap
msgid "Thumbnail Service *(tumbler)*"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:30
#, no-wrap
msgid "Some performance improvements for the pixbuf-thumbnailer and the scheduler were done. As well now there are multiple overwrite options for the desktop-thumbnailer.\n"
msgstr "Der blev lavet nogle forbedringer til ydelsen af pixbuf-thumbnailer og planlæggeren. Og der er nu adskillige valgmuligheder for overskrivning til desktop-thumbnailer.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:32
#, no-wrap
msgid "There is now support for the thumbnail sizes x-large and xx-large, which are very useful for high resolution displays.\n"
msgstr "Der er nu understøttelse af miniaturer i størrelse x-large og xx-large, hvilket er meget nyttigt på skærme med høj opløsning.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:34
#, no-wrap
msgid "Tumbler and Thunar now support shared thumbnail repositories, like described in the freedesktop.org thumbnail specification. This feature can be used to produce thumbnails for a folder in advance, directly located near the pictures. Like that, the thumbnails don't need to be re-generated for each individual user.\n"
msgstr "Tumbler og Thunar understøtter nu delte miniaturedepoter, som beskrevet i \"freedesktop.org thumbnail specification\". Funktionen kan bruges til at lave miniaturer til en mappe på forhånd, direkte placeret nær billederne. Så behøver miniaturerne ikke blive genereret igen for hver bruger.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:36
#, no-wrap
msgid "For more information on shared thumbnails, check the [related blog post](http://users.uoa.gr/~sdi1800073/sources/xfce_blog03.html).\n"
msgstr "Tjek [den relaterede blogpost](http://users.uoa.gr/~sdi1800073/sources/xfce_blog03.html) for mere information om delte miniaturer.\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour418.md:37 content/about/tour416.md:47
#: content/about/tour414.md:33 content/about/tour412.md:39
#: content/about/tour410.md:25 content/about/tour48.md:29
#: content/about/tour46.md:19
#, no-wrap
msgid "Panel *(xfce4-panel)*"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:40
#, no-wrap
msgid "The DateTime and the Clock plugins provided overlapping functionality. In order to prevent parallel development, they have been merged into a single plugin.\n"
msgstr "Pluginsene Dato og klokkeslæt og Ur gav overlappende funktionalitet. For at forhindre parallel udvikling er de blevet sammenlagt til ét plugin.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:42
#, no-wrap
msgid "![The new 'Clock' panel widget][img-panel-clock1]\n"
msgstr "![Den ny 'Ur'-panelwidget][img-panel-clock1]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:44
#, no-wrap
msgid "The new Clock plugin received a new binary time mode now and provides a sleep monitor. Here's a screenshot of all possible layouts which are: Analog, Binary, Digital, Fuzzy and LCD.\n"
msgstr "Det nye Ur-plugin har nu fået en ny tilstand til binær tid og har søvnovervågning. Her er et skærmbillede med alle layoutsne: analogt, binært, digitalt, upræcist og LCD.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:46
#, no-wrap
msgid "![All possible Clock Modes][img-panel-clock2]\n"
msgstr "![Alle ur-tilstande][img-panel-clock2]\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour418.md:47 content/about/tour412.md:55
#: content/about/tour410.md:99 content/about/tour46.md:9
#, no-wrap
msgid "Desktop Manager *(xfdesktop)*"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:50
#, no-wrap
msgid "Like in Thunar, the 'Delete' menu entry in the context menu can now be hidden.\n"
msgstr "Ligesom i Thunar, kan menupunktet 'Slet' nu skjules i genvejsmenuen.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:52
#, no-wrap
msgid "In order to don't mess the desktop by accident on pressing 'rearrange desktop icons', the user is asked for confirmation now.\n"
msgstr "For ikke at lave rod på skrivebordet ved en fejl når der trykkes på 'Opstil skrivebordsikoner', så skal brugeren nu bekræfte valget.\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour418.md:53 content/about/tour416.md:17
#: content/about/tour414.md:9
#, no-wrap
msgid "Settings Manager *(xfce4-settings)*"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:56
#, no-wrap
msgid "The search entry for xfce4-settings-manager was a bit simplified. Now it will always be shown, without any slider or button.\n"
msgstr "Søgeindtastningen i xfce4-settings-manager blev gjort lidt simplere. Nu bliver den altid vist, uden nogen skyder eller knap.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:58
#, no-wrap
msgid "![xfce4-settings-manager - the search entry is always shown][img-settings-main-dialog]\n"
msgstr "![xfce4-settings-manager - søgeindtastningen vises altid][img-settings-main-dialog]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:62
#, no-wrap
msgid "xfce4-display-settings got some minor improvements and the possibility to decide what to do when new displays are connected.\n"
msgstr "xfce4-display-settings fik nogle mindre forbedringer og mulighed for at beslutte hvad der skal ske når der tilsluttes nye skærme.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:64
#, no-wrap
msgid "![xfce4-display-settings - minor improvements][img-settings-display]\n"
msgstr "![xfce4-display-settings - mindre forbedringer][img-settings-display]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:68
#, no-wrap
msgid "On selecting a new theme, there is now the option to automatically set a matching xfwm4 theme, if available.\n"
msgstr "Når der vælges et nyt tema, så er der nu mulighed for automatisk at indstille et matchende xfwm4-tema, hvis det er tilgængeligt.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:70
#, no-wrap
msgid "![xfce4-appearance-settings - toggle to set matching Xfwm4 theme][img-settings-appearance]\n"
msgstr "![xfce4-appearance-settings - tilvælg for at matche Xfwm4-tema][img-settings-appearance]\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour418.md:71 content/about/tour416.md:41
#: content/about/tour414.md:55 content/about/tour412.md:105
#: content/about/tour410.md:49 content/about/tour48.md:9
#: content/about/tour46.md:67
#, no-wrap
msgid "File Manager *(thunar)*"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:76
#, no-wrap
msgid "For directories, the count of containing files can now be displayed in the size column. It is now possible to add a 'file creation date' column, and the 'configure columns' dialog can be opened with a right-click on any column head.\n"
msgstr "For mapper, kan antallet af filer i mappen nu vises i størrelse-kolonnen. Det er nu muligt at tilføje en 'filoprettelsesdato'-kolonne, og 'konfigurer kolonner'-dialogen kan åbnes ved at højreklikke på et af kolonnehovederne.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:78
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - List View - Preferences][img-thunar-listview1]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Listevisning - Præferencer][img-thunar-listview1]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:80
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - List View - File count and file creation date][img-thunar-listview2]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Listevisning - Antal filer og filoprettelsesdato][img-thunar-listview2]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour418.md:81
#, no-wrap
msgid "Image Preview"
msgstr "Forhåndsvisning af billeder"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:84
#, no-wrap
msgid "Finally, an image preview side pane has been added to Thunar. No, wait, actually two of them! You can choose to either use the 'embedded' mode which will take no extra space, but hide parts of the left side pane. Or you can go for the 'standalone' mode, which will use a separate pane on the right and display as well some basic information.\n"
msgstr "Der er endeligt blevet tilføjet en siderude til forhåndsvisning af billeder i Thunar. Nej vent ... der er faktisk to! Du kan enten vælge at bruge 'indlejret'-tilstand, som ikke optager ekstra plads men skjuler dele af det venstre sidepanel. Eller du kan vælge 'selvstændig'-tilstand, som bruger et separat panel i højre side og desuden viser nogle grundlæggende informationer.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:86
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - Embedded Image Preview][img-thunar-preview1]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Indlejret forhåndsvisning af billeder][img-thunar-preview1]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:88
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - Standalone Image Preview][img-thunar-preview2]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Selvstændig forhåndsvisning af billeder][img-thunar-preview2]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour418.md:89
#, no-wrap
msgid "Undo and Redo"
msgstr "Fortryd og omgør"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:92
#, no-wrap
msgid "It is now possible to undo basic file operations and to redo them. Undo and Redo can be used for 'move', 'rename', 'trash', 'link' and 'create' operations. Per default, a history of the last 10 operations is stored, though the history length is configurable. Whenever an Undo/Redo is triggered, a notification with few details will be shown.\n"
msgstr "Det er nu muligt at fortryde grundlæggende filhandlinger og omgøre dem. Fortryd og Omgør kan bruges til handlingerne 'flyt', 'omdøb', 'papirkurv', 'henvisning' og 'opret'. Som standard gemmes der en historik med de seneste 10 handlinger – historiklængden kan dog konfigureres. Når en Fortryd/Omgør udløses, så vises der en underretning med lidt detaljer.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:94
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - Undo and Redo][img-thunar-undo-redo]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Fortryd og omgør][img-thunar-undo-redo]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour418.md:95
#, no-wrap
msgid "File Highlight"
msgstr "Fremhævning af filer"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:98
#, no-wrap
msgid "Files now can be highlighted by setting the background and the filename to different colors. This can be done via an additional tab, located in the 'properties' dialog. The view menu provides a checkbox in order to enable/disable the feature. Once enabled, files now can be shown in all the colors of the rainbow.\n"
msgstr "Filer kan nu fremhæves ved at indstille baggrunden og filnavnet til forskellige farver. Det kan gøres via et ekstra faneblad som findes i dialogen 'egenskaber'. Vis-menuen har en afkrydsningsboks til at aktivere/deaktivere funktionaliteten. Når den er aktiveret, så kan filer vises i alle regnbuens farver.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:100
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - File Highlight Options][img-thunar-hightlight1]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Valgmuligheder for fremhævning af filer][img-thunar-hightlight1]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:102
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - Highlighted files in List View][img-thunar-hightlight2]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Fremhævede filer i listevisning][img-thunar-hightlight2]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:104
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - Highlighted files in Icon View][img-thunar-hightlight3]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Fremhævede filer i ikonvisning][img-thunar-hightlight3]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:106
#, no-wrap
msgid "For more information on file highlight, check the [related blog post](https://elessar-space.blogspot.com/2022/08/gsoc22-file-highlighting-in-thunar.html).\n"
msgstr "Tjek [den relaterede blogpost](https://elessar-space.blogspot.com/2022/08/gsoc22-file-highlighting-in-thunar.html) for mere information om fremhævning af filer.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:110
#, no-wrap
msgid "It is now possible to customize the toolbar according to your personal needs! An additional dialog has been added for that purpose, on which the visibility and position of specific items can be managed. As well custom actions, which appear for folders can be used in the toolbar.\n"
msgstr "Det er nu muligt at tilpasse værktøjslinjen efter dine personlige behov! Der er blevet tilføjet en ekstra dialog til formålet, hvor synligheden og placeringen af bestemte elementer kan håndteres. Tilpassede handlinger der vises for mapper kan også bruges i værktøjslinjen.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:112
#, no-wrap
msgid "When the menubar is hidden, an additional toolbar button which can be used to show the menu will be displayed.\n"
msgstr "Når menulinjen er skjult, så vises der yderligere en værktøjslinjeknap som kan bruges til at vise menuen.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:114
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - Toolbar with all configurable Elements][img-thunar-toolbar1]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Værktøjslinje med alle de elementer som kan konfigureres][img-thunar-toolbar1]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:116
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - Toolbar Configuration Dialog][img-thunar-toolbar2]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Dialog til konfiguration af værktøjslinje][img-thunar-toolbar2]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:118
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - Show Menubar button][img-thunar-toolbar3]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Vis menulinjeknap][img-thunar-toolbar3]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:120
#, no-wrap
msgid "For more information on the configurable toolbar, check the [related blog post](http://users.uoa.gr/~sdi1800073/sources/xfce_blog10.html).\n"
msgstr "Tjek [den relaterede blogpost](http://users.uoa.gr/~sdi1800073/sources/xfce_blog10.html) for mere information om den konfigurerbare værktøjslinje.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:124
#, no-wrap
msgid "Thunar now provides the option to use split panes. The pane separator can be moved, and its position will be stored. Via a xfconf setting, it is as well possible to have a vertical split.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:126
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - Split Panes][img-thunar-splitpanes]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Opdelte ruder][img-thunar-splitpanes]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:130
#, no-wrap
msgid "The status bar style was tweaked and '|' is now used to separate entries. Furthermore, it is now possible to customize it by using the context menu.\n"
msgstr "Statuslinjestilen er blevet finjusteret og '|' bruges nu til at adskille poster. Nu er det desuden muligt at tilpasse den ved at bruge genvejsmenuen.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:132
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - Statusbar Customization][img-thunar-statusbar]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Tilpasning af statuslinje][img-thunar-statusbar]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour418.md:133
#, no-wrap
msgid "Recursive Search"
msgstr "Rekursiv søgning"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:136
#, no-wrap
msgid "Thunar has now the possibility to search recursively, directly inside Thunar itself. The search is done in a separate thread and search results are added rapidly into a List View. A new row 'Location' shows where the search results are located, and the context menu provides the option 'Open Item Location' in order to travel there quickly. The preferences dialog provides an option to limit recursive search to local folders, or to disable it.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:138
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - Recursive Search][img-thunar-search1]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Rekursiv søgning][img-thunar-search1]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:140
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - Recursive Search Preferences][img-thunar-search2]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Præferencer for rekursiv søgning][img-thunar-search2]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:142
#, no-wrap
msgid "For more information on the recursive search feature, check the [related blog post](http://users.uoa.gr/~sdi1800073/sources/xfce_blog04.html).\n"
msgstr "Tjek [den relaterede blogpost](http://users.uoa.gr/~sdi1800073/sources/xfce_blog04.html) for mere information om funktionaliteten til rekursiv søgning.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour418.md:143
#, no-wrap
msgid "Recently used Files"
msgstr "Seneste brugte filer"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:146
#, no-wrap
msgid "Recently used files now can be accessed in the side pane. Like for the 'Recursive Search' feature, the new 'Location' row can be used in List View. Additionally, for 'Recent' a new row 'Recency' can be added to sort the files by their latest usage.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:148
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - Recently Used Files][img-thunar-recent]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Seneste brugte filer][img-thunar-recent]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:150
#, no-wrap
msgid "For more information on 'Recent' in Thunar check the [related blog post](http://users.uoa.gr/~sdi1800073/sources/xfce_blog02.html).\n"
msgstr "Tjek [den relaterede blogpost](http://users.uoa.gr/~sdi1800073/sources/xfce_blog02.html) for mere information om 'Seneste' i Thunar.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour418.md:151
#, no-wrap
msgid "Bookmark Menu"
msgstr "Bogmærkemenu"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:154
#, no-wrap
msgid "In order to keep the 'Go' menu compact, bookmarks have been moved into a separate, new 'Bookmarks' menu. The menu item 'add Bookmark' was rather hidden in the 'send to' menu in Thunar 4.18. As part of the new 'Bookmarks' menu, it is more prominent now.\n"
msgstr "For at holde 'Gå'-menuen kompakt er bogmærker blevet flyttet ind i en ny separat 'Bogmærker'-menu. Menupunktet 'Tilføj bogmærke' var ret skjult i 'send til'-menuen i Thunar 4.18. Som del af den nye 'Bogmærker'-menu er den nu mere fremtrædende.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:156
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - Bookmarks Menu][img-thunar-bookmarks]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Bogmærkemenu][img-thunar-bookmarks]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour418.md:157
#, no-wrap
msgid "Trash directory"
msgstr "Papirkurvens mappe"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:160
#, no-wrap
msgid "With the new release, the trash directory provides an info bar which gives easy access to `Empty Trash` and 'Restore' functionality. When using List View, a 'Date Deleted' column will be shown, so that the files can be sorted by deletion date. Via context menu, it is now possible to select 'Restore and Show' in order to automatically open a new tab in the folder of the restored file(s).\n"
msgstr "Med den nye udgivelse har papirkurvens mappe en infolinje der giver nem adgang til `Tøm papirkurv`- og 'Gendan'-funktionalitet. Når listevisning bruges vises der en ' Sletningsdato'-kolonne, så filerne kan sorteres efter sletningsdato. I genvejsmenuen er det nu muligt at vælge 'Gendan og vis' for automatisk at åbne mappen med de gendannede filer i et nyt faneblad.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:162
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - Trash Infobar and Date Deleted Column][img-thunar-trash]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Infolinje for papirkurv og kolonne for sletningsdato][img-thunar-trash]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour418.md:163 content/about/tour416.md:23
#, no-wrap
msgid "Default Applications"
msgstr "Standardprogrammer"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:166
#, no-wrap
msgid "The management to set/unset default applications for specific mime types was improved. The context menu got a dedicated item 'Set Default Application' which will open the 'ApplicationChooserDialog' with 'use as default' preselected. The dialog now has a section 'Default Application' in order to make clear which default application currently is set. If you want to remove applications from the list, right click it and select 'forget association'.\n"
msgstr "Håndteringen til at indstille/afindstille standardprogrammer for bestemte MIME-typer blev forbedret. Genvejsmenuen fik punktet 'Indstil standardprogram' som åbner 'ApplicationChooserDialog' med 'brug som standard' valgt på forhånd. Dialogen har nu afsnittet 'Standardprogram' for at gøre det tydeligt hvilket standardprogram som på nuværende tidspunkt er indstillet. Hvis du vil fjerne programmer fra listen, så højreklik på det og vælg 'glem program'.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:168
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - Context Menu Entry to set Default Application][img-thunar-default-application1]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Genvejsmenupunkt til indstilling af standardprogram][img-thunar-default-application1]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:170
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - Revamped Application Chooser Dialog][img-thunar-default-application2]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Nyt udseende i dialogen til at vælge program][img-thunar-default-application2]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:174
#, no-wrap
msgid "It is now possible to arrange custom actions in cascading submenus. Just enter the same submenu name for a custom action in order to place it into the same menu. If you require multiple menu levels, you can achieve that by using '/' in the path of the 'Submenu' entry.\n"
msgstr "Det er nu muligt at opstille tilpassede handlinger i undermenuer der foldes ud. Indtast blot navnet på den samme undermenu til en tilpassede handling for at placere den i den samme menu. Hvis du har brug for flere menuniveauer, så kan du opnå det ved at bruge '/' i stien til 'Submenu'-punktet.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:176
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - Custom Action Submenu][img-thunar-uca-submenu1]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Undermenu for tilpasset handlinger][img-thunar-uca-submenu1]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:178
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - Custom Action Configuration Dialog][img-thunar-uca-submenu2]\n"
msgstr "![Konfigurationsdialog for tilpasset handlinger][img-thunar-uca-submenu2]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:182
#, no-wrap
msgid "The thumbnail settings in the preferences dialog got grouped together, and meanwhile it is possible to limit the file size for which thumbnails should be generated. That should mitigate possible performance issues by preventing thumbnail generation for huge video files.\n"
msgstr "Miniatureindstillingerne i præferencer-dialogen blev grupperet og samtidigt er det muligt at begrænse filstørrelsen for hvornår der genereres miniaturer. Det burde fjerne eventuelle ydelsesproblemer ved at forhindre generering af miniaturer for kæmpe videofiler.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:184
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - Thumbnail Preferences][img-thunar-preferences1]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Præferencer for miniaturer][img-thunar-preferences1]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:186
#, no-wrap
msgid "File transfer operations optionally can use *.partial~ as an intermediate file now. After a transfer operation, there is now the option to verify the file checksums in order to make sure that no single bit got corrupted. Note that the checksum feature will require some extra time during copy when activated.\n"
msgstr "Filoverførselshandlinger kan nu valgfrit bruge *.partial~ som en mellemliggende fil. Efter en overførselshandling er der mulighed for at bekræfte filens tjeksum for at sikre at der ikke er en eneste bit som er blevet beskadiget. Bemærk at tjeksum-funktionaliteten kræver ekstra tid under kopiering når den er aktiveret.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:188
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - File Transfer Preferences][img-thunar-preferences2]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Præferencer for filoverførsel][img-thunar-preferences2]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:190
#, no-wrap
msgid "For more information on the new file transfer options, check the [related blog post](https://dev.ikx.kr/GSOC-5th/).\n"
msgstr "Tjek [den relaterede blogpost](https://dev.ikx.kr/GSOC-5th/) for mere information om de nye valgmuligheder for filoverførsel.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:192
#, no-wrap
msgid "A checkbox was added in order to allow running shell scripts. In Thunar 4.18 it only was possible to change that behavior by changing a hidden setting. Use that option with caution!\n"
msgstr "Der blev tilføjet en afkrydsningsboks for at gøre det muligt at køre skal-scripter. I Thunar 4.18 var det kun muligt at ændre opførslen ved at ændre en hemmelig indstilling. Vær forsigtig når valgmuligheden bruges!\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:194
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - Script Execution Preferences][img-thunar-preferences3]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Præferencer for udførsel af scripts][img-thunar-preferences3]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:196
#, no-wrap
msgid "There is now the possibility to restore tabs on startup, and to show the full directory path in the tab title.\n"
msgstr "Det er nu muligt at gendanne faneblade under opstart, og at vise den fule mappesti i fanebladets titel.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:198
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - Tab and Window Preferences][img-thunar-preferences4]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Præferencer for faneblade og vinduer][img-thunar-preferences4]\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour418.md:199 content/about/tour410.md:17
#: content/about/tour46.md:131
#, no-wrap
msgid "Application Finder *(xfce4-appfinder)*"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour418.md:201
#, no-wrap
msgid "Configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguration"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:204
#, no-wrap
msgid "Application Finder got support for the 'PrefersNonDefaultGPU' property, which is useful for systems with hybrid graphic cards.\n"
msgstr "Programfinder fik understøttelse af 'PrefersNonDefaultGPU'-egenskaben, som kan anvendes på systemer med hybrid grafikkort.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:206
#, no-wrap
msgid "Environment variables are now parsed when passed in collapsed mode.\n"
msgstr "Miljøvariabler fortolkes nu når de videregives i sammenfoldet tilstand.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour418.md:207
#, no-wrap
msgid "Appearance"
msgstr "Udseende"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:210
#, no-wrap
msgid "An option to hide the window decorations was added.\n"
msgstr "Der blev tilføjet en valgmulighed til at skjule vinduedekorationerne.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:212
#, no-wrap
msgid "![xfce4-appfinder without window decorations][img-appfinder]\n"
msgstr "![xfce4-appfinder uden vinduesdekorationer][img-appfinder]\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour418.md:213 content/about/tour412.md:9
#: content/about/tour410.md:107 content/about/tour46.md:43
#, no-wrap
msgid "Window Manager *(xfwm4)*"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour418.md:215
#, no-wrap
msgid "Workspaces"
msgstr "Arbejdsområder"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:218
#, no-wrap
msgid "Workspace setting will now work as well with other window managers.\n"
msgstr "Arbejdsområdeindstilling virker nu også med andre vindueshåndteringer.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour418.md:219
#, no-wrap
msgid "Compositor"
msgstr "Kompositør"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:222
#, no-wrap
msgid "The compositor now supports adaptive vsync with GLX.\n"
msgstr "Kompositøren understøtter nu adaptiv vsync med GLX.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:228
#, no-wrap
msgid "Improved support for UI scaling and fix for many blurry icons in the core components when scaling is used. This will be particularly useful for Hi DPI screens.\n"
msgstr "Forbedret understøttelse af brugerfladeskalering og rettelse af mange utydelige ikoner i kernekomponenter når der bruges skalering. Det vil særligt være nyttigt på skærme med høj DPI.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour418.md:229
#, no-wrap
msgid "Window Header Bars"
msgstr "Headerlinjer for vinduer"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:232
#, no-wrap
msgid "All header bars of Xfce Windows/Dialogs by default will be drawn by the window manager now (Xfwm4). Some dialogs optionally support 'GtkHeaderBar' (CSD) which can be enabled via a xfconf setting.\n"
msgstr "Alle headerlinjer i Xfce-vinduer/-dialoger tegnes nu som standard af vindueshåndteringen (Xfwm4). Nogle dialoger understøtter valgfrit 'GtkHeaderBar' (CSD) som kan aktiveres via en xfconf-indstilling.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:234
#, no-wrap
msgid "![xfce-appearance-settings - Preference to enable GtkHeaderBar][img-general-gtkheaderbar]\n"
msgstr "![xfce-appearance-settings - Præference til at aktivere GtkHeaderBar][img-general-gtkheaderbar]\n"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: title
#: content/about/tour416.md:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce 4.16 tour"
msgstr "Xfce 4.16 rundvisning"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour416.md:8
#, no-wrap
msgid "This tour will introduce you to new major features of Xfce 4.16. It only covers improvements made on the (user-visible) surface; for the full list of changes, see the [changelog](/download/changelogs/4.16/).\n"
msgstr "Denne rundvisning introducerer dig for nye større funktionaliteter i Xfce 4.16. Den dækker kun forbedringer som er lavet på overfladen (det som brugeren kan se); se [ændringsloggen](/download/changelogs/4.16/) for en komplet liste med ændringer.\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour416.md:9
#, no-wrap
msgid "Visual identity: New icons and palette"
msgstr "Visuel identitet: Nye ikoner og palet"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour416.md:12
#, no-wrap
msgid "In order to make Xfce shine a little more out of the box and to strengthen its visual identity we created new icons for all of our core applications and based them on a shared palette to ensure consistency. We also set some further (implicit) design constraints, loosely following Adwaita's principles.\n"
msgstr "For at få Xfce til at skinne lidt mere fra begyndelsen og for at styrke dens visuelle identitet har vi skabt nye ikoner til alle vores kerneprogrammer og baseret dem på en delt palet for at sikre ensartethed. Vi har også indstillet nogle ekstra (underforstået) designbegrænsninger der følger Adwaitas principper løst.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour416.md:14
#, no-wrap
msgid "![The Xfce palette][img-palette]\n"
msgstr "![Xfce-paletten][img-palette]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour416.md:16
#, no-wrap
msgid "![New upstream Xfce icons, coming in many sizes for sharp appearance][img-upstream-icons]\n"
msgstr "![Nye Xfce-ikoner i mange størrelser der giver et skarpt udseende][img-upstream-icons]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour416.md:20
#, no-wrap
msgid "The Settings Manager itself received a visual refresh of its filter box, which can now be hidden permanently. At the same time the search capabilities of the filter box were improved by searching the descriptive 'Comments' part of each dialog's launcher (aka [.desktop](https://specifications.freedesktop.org/desktop-entry-spec/desktop-entry-spec-latest.html)) file.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour416.md:22
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Visually cleaner, more powerful filter box][img-settings-manager]\n"
msgstr "![Visuelt renere og mere kraftfuld filterboks][img-settings-manager]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour416.md:26
#, no-wrap
msgid "This new dialog represents a merger between the previously available 'Mime Settings' and the 'Preferred Applications' dialogs. Consolidating both in one place means users have an easier time setting default applications to handle certain file types.\n"
msgstr "Den nye dialog er en sammenlægning af dialogerne 'Mime-indstillinger' og 'Foretrukne programmer' der fandtes tidligere. At de begge er samlet ét sted betyder at brugerne lettere kan indstille standardprogrammer til at håndtere bestemte filtyper.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour416.md:28
#, no-wrap
msgid "![The new Default Applications dialog][img-default-applications]\n"
msgstr "![Den ny dialog Standardprogrammer][img-default-applications]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour416.md:29 content/about/tour414.md:17
#, no-wrap
msgid "Display Dialog"
msgstr "Dialogen Skærm"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour416.md:32
#, no-wrap
msgid "To better support high-density displays - which come in various sizes and densities - we added fractional scaling based on the RandR extension of X11. Furthermore the preferred mode of a display is now marked with an asterisk and aspect ratios are shown along display resolutions.\n"
msgstr "For bedre at understøtte skærme med høj tæthed - der findes i forskellige størrelser og tætheder - har vi tilføjet skalering med kommatal baseret på X11's RandR-udvidelse. Derudover er den foretrukne tilstand for en skærm nu markeret med en stjerne og højde-/breddeforhold vises sammen med skærmopløsninger.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour416.md:34
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Fractional scaling support][img-display-dialog]\n"
msgstr "![Understøttelse af skalering med kommatal][img-display-dialog]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour416.md:35
#, no-wrap
msgid "Keyboard Shortcuts"
msgstr "Tastaturgenveje"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour416.md:38
#, no-wrap
msgid "In order to make things easier for our users we added more default keyboard shortcuts out of the box, for instance for window tiling or to open Thunar. The keyboard shortcuts dialog itself was also visually updated.\n"
msgstr "For at gøre tingene lettere for vores brugere har vi tilføjet flere standardtastaturgenveje fra begyndelsen, f.eks. til fliselægning af vinduer og til at åbne Thunar. Tastaturgenvejsdialogen er også blevet fornyet visuelt.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour416.md:40
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Visually updated keyboard shortcuts dialog][img-keyboard-shortcuts]\n"
msgstr "![Visuelt opdateret tastaturgenvejsdialog][img-keyboard-shortcuts]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour416.md:44
#, no-wrap
msgid "In Thunar's copy and move dialogs users can now easily pause the respective file operation. Furthermore support for queued file transfer, remembering view settings per folder and support for transparency in Gtk themes was added.\n"
msgstr "I Thunars kopiér- og flyt-dialoger kan brugerne nu let pause den pågældende filhandling. Derudover er der tilføjet understøttelse af filoverførsel i kø, visningsindstillinger kan huskes pr. mappe og understøttelse af gennemsigtighed i Gtk-temaer.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour416.md:46
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar can now pause copying/moving files][img-thunar-copy]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar kan nu sætte filer der kopieres/flyttes på pause][img-thunar-copy]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour416.md:50
#, no-wrap
msgid "The panel received quite a few noteworthy updates, an animation for autohide and intellihide, a new 'Status Tray' plugin that combines both legacy Systray item support with modern StatusNotifier item support, dark mode support, launchers showing additional actions on right-click, window buttons offering to 'Launch a new instance...' and much more.\n"
msgstr "Panelet modtog ret mange bemærkelsesværdige opdateringer, en animation til automatisk skjul og intelligent skjul, et nyt 'statusbakke'-plugin der kombinerer både understøttelse af forældede elementer for systembakke med understøttelse af moderne elementer for statusunderretter, understøttelse af mørk tilstand, startere viser yderligere handlinger ved højreklik, vinduesknapper der med 'Start en ny instans ...' og meget mere.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour416.md:52
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Dark mode enabled in the panel's settings dialog][img-panel-dark]\n"
msgstr "![Mørk tilstand aktiveret i panelets indstillingsdialog][img-panel-dark]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour416.md:54
#, no-wrap
msgid "![The new statustray plugin][img-panel-statustray]\n"
msgstr "![Det nye statusbakke-plugin][img-panel-statustray]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour416.md:56
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Autohide animation][img-panel-autohide]\n"
msgstr "![Animation med automatisk skjul][img-panel-autohide]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour416.md:58
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Launch a new instance!][img-panel-launch]\n"
msgstr "![Start en ny instans!][img-panel-launch]\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour416.md:59
#, no-wrap
msgid "About Dialog *(xfce4-about)*"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour416.md:62
#, no-wrap
msgid "Not only was the Xfce tab reworked to be more visually appealing and easily parsable, a separate tab showing basic information about the user's system was also added.\n"
msgstr "Der er ikke kun blevet arbejdet på Xfce-fanebladet for at gøre det mere visuelt tiltalende, et separat faneblad der viser grundlæggende information om brugerens system er også blevet tilføjet.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour416.md:64
#, no-wrap
msgid "![About Xfce][img-about-xfce]\n"
msgstr "![Om Xfce][img-about-xfce]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour416.md:66
#, no-wrap
msgid "![About System][img-about-system]\n"
msgstr "![Om systemet][img-about-system]\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour416.md:67 content/about/tour414.md:69
#: content/about/tour412.md:81
#, no-wrap
msgid "Power Manager *(xfce4-power-manager)*"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour416.md:70
#, no-wrap
msgid "The settings dialog of the power manager was cleaned up and shows either 'on battery' or 'plugged in' settings as opposed to both in a huge table.\n"
msgstr "Der er blevet ryddet op i strømstyringens indstillingsdialog og der vises enten indstillingen 'på batteri' eller 'tilsluttet' i modsætning til begge i en stor tabel.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour416.md:72
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Power Manager settings][img-powermanager]\n"
msgstr "![Strømstyringsindstillinger][img-powermanager]\n"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: title
#: content/about/tour414.md:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce 4.14 tour"
msgstr "Xfce 4.14 rundvisning"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:8
#, no-wrap
msgid "This tour will introduce you to new major features of Xfce 4.14. It only covers improvements made on the surface; for the full list of changes, see the [changelogs](/download/changelogs/).\n"
msgstr "Denne rundvisning introducerer dig for nye større funktionaliteter i Xfce 4.14. Den dækker kun forbedringer som er lavet på overfladen; se [ændringsloggene](/download/changelogs/) for en fuld liste af ændringer.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour414.md:11
#, no-wrap
msgid "Color Profiles Dialog"
msgstr "Dialogen Farveprofiler"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:14
#, no-wrap
msgid "A new dialog for setting [color profiles](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfce4-settings/4.14/color) for monitors, printers and scanners was introduced. It acts as a frontend to various daemons that talk directly to colord, e.g. saned (scanners), cupsd (printers) or xiccd (monitors).\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:16
#, no-wrap
msgid "![The new color profiles dialog][img-color-profiles]\n"
msgstr "![Den nye dialog med farveprofiler][img-color-profiles]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:20
#, no-wrap
msgid "Several improvements were made to the [display dialog](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfce4-settings/4.14/display). Apart from tweaks to the user interface to make the interaction more intuitive (introducing display numbering, showing a primary indicator with quick access to panel, notification and desktop settings etc.) a feature to save and restore complete display profiles was added. If a single profile exists for a setup, the Xfce settings daemon will automatically enable it. If multiple profiles exist, it will pop up the minimal dialog and offer all profiles in addition to the previously available pre-sets (internal only, mirror, extend and external only).\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:22
#, no-wrap
msgid "![The primary indicator][img-display-general]\n"
msgstr "![Indikatoren for primær][img-display-general]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:24
#, no-wrap
msgid "![The display profile list][img-display-advanced]\n"
msgstr "![Listen over skærmprofiler][img-display-advanced]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:26
#, no-wrap
msgid "![The improved minimal dialog - in this case only showing one profile only which never happens anymore now ;)][img-display-minimal]\n"
msgstr "![Den forbedrede minimale dialog - i dette tilfælde vises kun én profil som nu aldrig sker længere ;)][img-display-minimal]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour414.md:27
#, no-wrap
msgid "Accessibility"
msgstr "Tilgængelighed"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:30
#, no-wrap
msgid "One [accessibility](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfce4-settings/4.14/accessibility) feature that people coming from other desktop environments or operating systems were still missing is to set a (custom) keyboard shortcut (by default: Super+F1) to visually locate the mouse pointer. This feature was added in Xfce 4.14.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:32
#, no-wrap
msgid "![The mouse pointer location animation][img-locate-mouse]\n"
msgstr "![Animation med musemarkørens placering][img-locate-mouse]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour414.md:35
#, no-wrap
msgid "General: Icon size"
msgstr "Generelt: Ikonstørrelse"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:38
#, no-wrap
msgid "A new feature that we introduced in the [panel](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfce4-panel/4.14/start) is being able to control the icon size of all plugins. ('All' may not be technically correct, as not all plugins support the new API as of now, but now they *can*. Plus the Window buttons plugin is an exception, because libwnck doesn't allow anything other than 16px or 32px.) This means setups that were previously impossible, because icons would upscale automatically according to size-steps hard-coded in the panel, are now possible (see below).\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:40
#, no-wrap
msgid "![A 32px tall panel with 16px icons][img-panel-iconsize]\n"
msgstr "![Et panel med en højde på 32 px med 16 px ikoner][img-panel-iconsize]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour414.md:41
#, no-wrap
msgid "Window buttons: Grouping"
msgstr "Vinduesknapper: Gruppering"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:44
#, no-wrap
msgid "Grouping was improved in the [Window buttons plugin](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfce4-panel/4.14/tasklist), both functionally (by improving the matching and icon-finding) and visually by providing a new group indicator that is less likely to clash with window titles containing an enumeration in brackets.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:46
#, no-wrap
msgid "![The new group indicator (two terminal windows)][img-panel-group]\n"
msgstr "![Den nye gruppeindikator (to terminalvinduer)][img-panel-group]\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour414.md:47
#, no-wrap
msgid "Session *(xfce4-session)*"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour414.md:49 content/about/tour412.md:89
#, no-wrap
msgid "Settings Dialog"
msgstr "Indstillingsdialog"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:52
#, no-wrap
msgid "As soon as a [session](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfce4-session/4.14/preferences) has been saved a new tab is dynamically added to the settings dialog displaying all saved sessions and allowing to delete one or all of them. This should make it way more discoverable for users if they actually have saved sessions that influence the startup behavior - previously this had to be checked manually in the filesystem.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:54
#, no-wrap
msgid "![The settings dialog after saving a session][img-session-saved]\n"
msgstr "![Indstillingsdialogen efter en session er blevet gemt][img-session-saved]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour414.md:57
#, no-wrap
msgid "Pathbar"
msgstr "Stilinje"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:60
#, no-wrap
msgid "Up to Xfce 4.12 [Thunar](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/thunar/4.14/start) offered two options for the pathbar/locationbar. The best of both worlds has now been mixed into one powerful pathbar, featuring both clickable breadcrumbs (i.e. folders), an easily accessible way to hand-type a path as well as an improved look.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:62
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar's new pathbar][img-thunar-pathbar]\n"
msgstr "![Thunars nye stilinje][img-thunar-pathbar]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour414.md:63
#, no-wrap
msgid "Folder Thumbnailer"
msgstr "Miniaturer for mapper"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:66
#, no-wrap
msgid "Same as on the Desktop you can now save an image with the name 'folder.jpg' in a folder and get it displayed as its icon in the File Manager. Note: [Please read the docs](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/tumbler/available_plugins#customized_thumbnailer_for_folders) on how to set this up (if your distribution hasn't enabled it by default).\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:68
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar's new folder thumbnails][img-thunar-folder-jpg]\n"
msgstr "![Thunars nye miniaturer for mapper][img-thunar-folder-jpg]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour414.md:71 content/about/tour414.md:85
#: content/about/tour412.md:83
#, no-wrap
msgid "Panel Plugin"
msgstr "Panelplugin"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:74
#, no-wrap
msgid "The [Power Manager's panel plugin](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfce4-power-manager/4.14/panel-plugin) supports symbolic icons now and uses the standard UPower icon names (making it more compatible with all icon themes). It also shows an indicator if applications inhibit power management functions like suspend (when power is low) or display dimming (after a defined timeout).\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:76
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Parole's video playback is inhibiting power management][img-xfpm-inhibitors]\n"
msgstr "![Paroles videoafspilning forhindrer strømstyring][img-xfpm-inhibitors]\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour414.md:77
#, no-wrap
msgid "Notification Service *(xfce4-notifyd)*"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour414.md:79 content/about/tour44.md:123
#, no-wrap
msgid "Settings"
msgstr "Indstillinger"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:82
#, no-wrap
msgid "Several new features have been added in Xfce's [Notification service](https://docs.xfce.org/apps/notifyd/start), including a notifications log, the possibility to disable notifications per application, a global 'Do Not Disturb' mode, which inhibits all notifications, and finally a new animation ('slide out').\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:84
#, no-wrap
msgid "![The new notification animation 'slide out'][img-notifyd-slideout]\n"
msgstr "![Den ny underretningsanimation 'glid ud'][img-notifyd-slideout]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:88
#, no-wrap
msgid "Furthermore a new panel plugin was added which provides quick access to both the 'Do Not Disturb' mode as well as the log of recent notifications.\n"
msgstr "Derudover er der tilføjet et nyt panelplugin som giver hurtig adgang til både 'Forstyr ikke'-tilstanden samt loggen over seneste underretninger.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:90
#, no-wrap
msgid "![The new panel plugin][img-notifyd-panel]\n"
msgstr "![Det nye panelplugin][img-notifyd-panel]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour414.md:91 content/about/tour412.md:141
#, no-wrap
msgid "Media Player *(parole)*"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour414.md:93
#, no-wrap
msgid "Mini Mode"
msgstr "Minitilstand"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:96
#, no-wrap
msgid "[Parole](https://docs.xfce.org/apps/parole/start) now features a 'Mini Mode', where the interface is simplified to just display the album artwork and can be positioned over other windows without getting in the way.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:98
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Just right-click anywhere in the player window to select 'Mini Mode'...][img-parole-normal-mode]\n"
msgstr "![Du skal bare højreklikke et vilkårligt sted i afspillerens vindue og vælge 'Minitilstand' ...][img-parole-normal-mode]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:100
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Afterwards, enjoy a truly minimalistic playback experience!][img-parole-mini-mode]\n"
msgstr "![Herefter kan du nyde en rigtig minimalistisk afspilningsoplevelse!][img-parole-mini-mode]\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour414.md:101
#, no-wrap
msgid "Screensaver *(xfce4-screensaver)*"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour414.md:103
#, no-wrap
msgid "A Modern Locking Experience"
msgstr "En oplevelse med moderne udseende"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:106
#, no-wrap
msgid "The new Xfce [Screensaver](https://docs.xfce.org/apps/screensaver/start) provides a configurable lockscreen experience. You can selectively toggle the lock screen and screensaver, and all Xscreensaver themes are supported (with configuration options) out of the box. If you prefer a blank screen, Xfce Screensaver also includes a blank screen option with DPMS integration.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:108
#, no-wrap
msgid "![The new lock screen, sharing styles with LightDM GTK+ Greeter for a consistent experience.][img-saver-dialog]\n"
msgstr "![Den nye låseskærm i samme stil som LightDM GTK+ Greeter for en ensartet oplevelse.][img-saver-dialog]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:110
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Make it your own. Xfce Screensaver supports a multitude of configuration options.][img-saver-preferences]\n"
msgstr "![Gør den til din egen. Xfce Pauseskærm understøtter et væld af konfigurationsvalgmuligheder.][img-saver-preferences]\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour414.md:111
#, no-wrap
msgid "Terminal *(xfce4-terminal)*"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:114
#, no-wrap
msgid "Lots and lots of features have accumulated in the [Terminal](https://docs.xfce.org/apps/terminal/start) over the last years. Amongst them 'Undo Close Tab' and 'Close Other Tabs' functionality (similar to web browsers), 'Copy Input to All Tabs', 'Set Title Color' (allows to customize tab text color), 'Save Contents' (saves tab contents to a file), an 'Unsafe Paste' dialog (which prevents the terminal from auto-executing pasted text as a command) and support for zooming. Finally when closing a tab or window, there is a new check for running processes which prevents accidentally closing a terminal that is running a process.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:116
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Zooming, 'Save Contents' and much more!][img-terminal]\n"
msgstr "![Zoom, 'Gem indhold' og meget mere!][img-terminal]\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour414.md:117
#, no-wrap
msgid "Screenshooter *(xfce4-screenshooter)*"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:120
#, no-wrap
msgid "The Xfce [Screenshooter](https://docs.xfce.org/apps/screenshooter/start) gained several notable features, amongst others seeing the size of the screenshot while dragging, moving the selection with the mouse and better [imgur](https://imgur.com) integration.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:122
#, no-wrap
msgid "![I can drag and move the screenshot area, whoop whoop!][img-screenshooter]\n"
msgstr "![Jeg kan trække og flytte skærmbilledområdet, hurra hurra!][img-screenshooter]\n"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: title
#: content/about/tour412.md:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce 4.12 tour"
msgstr "Xfce 4.12 rundvisning"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:8
#, no-wrap
msgid "This tour will introduce you to new major features of Xfce 4.12. It only covers improvements made on the surface; for the full list of changes, see the [changelogs](/download/changelogs/).\n"
msgstr "Denne rundvisning introducerer dig for nye større funktionaliteter i Xfce 4.12. Den dækker kun forbedringer som er lavet på overfladen; se [ændringsloggene](/download/changelogs/) for en komplet liste med ændringer.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour412.md:11
#, no-wrap
msgid "Window Switcher Dialog"
msgstr "Vinduesskifter-dialog"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:14
#, no-wrap
msgid "The window manager's Alt+Tab dialog is now fully themeable and also gained two new modes: a 'List' mode and a 'Window Preview' mode. Furthermore users use their mouse to click/select the window they want to give focus to.\n"
msgstr "Vindueshåndteringens Alt+Tabulator-dialog kan nu fuldtud bruge temaer og har også fået to nye tilstande: En 'Liste'-tilstand og en 'Vinduesforhåndsvisning'-tilstand. Derudover kan brugere bruge deres mus til at klikke/vælge det vindue de vil give fokus til.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:16
#, no-wrap
msgid "![The traditional dialog is fully themable now][img-tabwin-simple-crop]\n"
msgstr "![Den traditionelle dialog kan nu fuldtud bruge temaer][img-tabwin-simple-crop]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:18
#, no-wrap
msgid "The List mode of the Alt-Tab dialog.\n"
msgstr "Listetilstanden i Alt-Tabulator-dialogen.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:20
#, no-wrap
msgid "![List mode of Alt-Tab, showing all window titles][img-tabwin-list-crop]\n"
msgstr "![Listetilstande i Alt-Tabulator, hvor alle vinduestitler vises][img-tabwin-list-crop]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:22
#, no-wrap
msgid "The Window Preview mode shows thumbnails of windows' content alongside their icon. Activating the compositor is a prerequisite for this mode.\n"
msgstr "Vinduesforhåndsvisningstilstanden viser miniaturer af vinduernes indhold sammen med deres ikon. Aktivering af kompositøren er påkrævet for at bruge denne tilstand.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:24
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Window thumbnails][img-tabwin-preview-crop]\n"
msgstr "![Vinduesminiaturer][img-tabwin-preview-crop]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour412.md:25
#, no-wrap
msgid "Tiling, Zooming, Client-side Decorations"
msgstr "Fliselægning, zoom, klientside-dekorationer"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:28
#, no-wrap
msgid "Support for Client-Side Decorations (CSDs) has been improved. They now properly snap to screen and panel borders, and tile correctly, even with shadows.\n"
msgstr "Understøttelse af klientside-dekorationer (CSD'er) er blevet forbedret. De fastgør sig nu korrekt til skærmen og panelernes kanter og fliselægger sig korrekt, selv med skygger.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:30
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Gtk3 apps with their decorations drawn by the client][img-xfwm4-csd]\n"
msgstr "![Gtk3-programmer hvor deres dekorationer er tegnet af klienten][img-xfwm4-csd]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:32
#, no-wrap
msgid "Window tiling mode was improved by providing support for corner-tiling, and a new zooming mode was added using Alt + Mouse Wheel.\n"
msgstr "Vindue-tilering måden var forbedret ved at forsyne understøttelse for hjørne-tilering, og en ny zooming funktion var tilføjet ved brug af Alt + Mus-hjulet.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:34
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Drag and drop a window to a corner to tile it][img-xfwm4-tiling-small]\n"
msgstr "![Træk og slip et vindue til et hjørne for at fliselægge det][img-xfwm4-tiling-small]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour412.md:35
#, no-wrap
msgid "HiDPI Support"
msgstr "HiDPI-understøttelse"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:38
#, no-wrap
msgid "In order to better support modern hi-resolution screens, two new Xfwm4 themes were added (hdpi, xhdpi).\n"
msgstr "For bedre at understøtte moderne højopløsningsskærme blev to nye Xfwm4-temaer tilføjet (hdpi, xhdpi).\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour412.md:41
#, no-wrap
msgid "Intelligent Hiding"
msgstr "Intelligent skjul"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:44
#, no-wrap
msgid "The panel can now intelligently hide itself when a window is dragged near it.\n"
msgstr "Panelet kan nu intelligent skjule sig selv når et vindue trækkes i nærheden af det.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:46
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Oh what is this window??][img-panel-shown]\n"
msgstr "![Hvad er dog dette vindue??][img-panel-shown]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:48
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Don't come closer!][img-panel-shown-stack]\n"
msgstr "![Kom ikke tættere på!][img-panel-shown-stack]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:50
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Hah! Now you don't see me!][img-panel-hidden]\n"
msgstr "![Ha! Nu kan du ikke se mig!][img-panel-hidden]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour412.md:51
#, no-wrap
msgid "Gtk3 plugins"
msgstr "Gtk3-plugins"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:54
#, no-wrap
msgid "Infrastructure was added to be able to load Gtk3 plugins alongside Gtk2 plugins.\n"
msgstr "Infrastruktur blev tilføjet for at gøre det muligt at indlæse Gtk3-plugins sammen med Gtk2-plugins.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:58
#, no-wrap
msgid "The desktop has a new wallpaper settings dialog with many new options and better multi-monitor support. Drag the dialog to the display or workspace where you want to change the wallpaper.\n"
msgstr "Skrivebordet har ny baggrund-indstillingers dialog med mange nye muligheder og bedre dobbelt-skærm understøttelse, Træk dialogen til skærmen eller arbejdsrummet hvor du vil ændre baggrunden.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:60
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Better multi-monitor support][img-xfdesktop-properties-multiworkspace]\n"
msgstr "![Bedre multiskærm-understøttelse][img-xfdesktop-properties-multiworkspace]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:62
#, no-wrap
msgid "Uncheck 'apply to all workspaces' to set a different wallpaper for each workspace.\n"
msgstr "Fravælg 'anvend på alle arbejdsområder' for at sætte et forskelligt tapet på hver arbejdsområde.\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour412.md:63 content/about/tour410.md:63
#: content/about/tour48.md:73 content/about/tour46.md:85
#, no-wrap
msgid "Settings *(xfce4-settings)*"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:68
#, no-wrap
msgid "Support for multi-monitor use was vastly improved in the display settings dialog. Upon connecting a new display, a quick setup popup offers some of the most-used modes for users to quickly change their layout.\n"
msgstr "Understøttelse for dobbeltskærms-brug var blevet enormt forbedret i skærm-indstillinger dialogen. Ved at forbinde ny skærm, dukker en indstillings-popup som tilbyder nogle af de mest brugte metoder for brugere der hurtigt vil skifte deres opsætning.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:70
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Configure multiple displays][img-xfce4-display-settings-twoscreens]\n"
msgstr "![Konfigurer flere skærme][img-xfce4-display-settings-twoscreens]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:72
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Choose your layout when plugging in a new display][img-xfce4-display-layout]\n"
msgstr "![Vælg dit layout når en ny skærm tilsluttes][img-xfce4-display-layout]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:76
#, no-wrap
msgid "The appearance dialog now showcases previews for styles and icons.\n"
msgstr "Udseendedialogen viser nu forhåndsvisningseksempler til stile og ikoner.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:78
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Gtk style preview][img-xfce4-appearance-settings-style]\n"
msgstr "![Forhåndsvisning af Gtk-stil][img-xfce4-appearance-settings-style]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:80
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Icon theme preview][img-xfce4-appearance-settings-icons]\n"
msgstr "![Forhåndsvisning af ikontema][img-xfce4-appearance-settings-icons]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:86
#, no-wrap
msgid "A new panel plugin was created which allows you to quickly control your screen brightness, either via the menu or by simply using your mouse's scroll wheel over the plugin. The plugin's menu also shows all other connected devices with a power status, e.g. bluetooth keyboards or wireless mice. It still offers quick access to the presentation mode, which inhibits your screensaver for as long as the option is active.\n"
msgstr "En ny plugin var skabt, som tillader dig hurtigt at kontrollere din skærms lysstyrke, enten via menuen eller mere simpelt ved brug af muse-hjulet over pluginet. Plugin's menuen viser også alle andre forbundede enheder med en strøm status f.eks bluetooth tastatur eller trådløse mus. Det tilbyder stadig hurtig adgang til præsentations-måden, som undgår din pauseskærm så længe som indstillingens-muligheden er aktiv.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:88
#, no-wrap
msgid "![The plugin's menu allows users to control screen brightness and check on the remaining uptime their battery provides.][img-xfpm-plugin-crop]\n"
msgstr "![Plugins menuen tillader brugere at kontrollere skærmens lysstyrke og tjekke oppetid som deres batteri tilbyder.][img-xfpm-plugin-crop]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:92
#, no-wrap
msgid "The settings dialog was completely restructured (separating button/lid events from system and display behavior) and offers a clearer way of setting your preferences.\n"
msgstr "Indstillings-dialogen var fuldstændig omstruktureret (separat knap/låg begivenheder fra system og skærm opførsel) og tilbyder en klar måde at sætte din indstillings-præference.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:94
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Configure what action to take when certain buttons are pressed or the laptop lid is closed][img-xfpm-prefs-general]\n"
msgstr "![Konfigurer hvilken aktion at tage når bestemte knapper er trykket eller når bærbares låg er lukket][img-xfpm-prefs-general]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:96
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Configure what to do when the user is inactive or battery is drained][img-xfpm-prefs-system]\n"
msgstr "![Konfigurer hvad der skal ske når brugeren er inaktiv eller batteriet er afladt][img-xfpm-prefs-system]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:98
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Manage display power management][img-xfpm-prefs-display]\n"
msgstr "![Håndter skræmstrømstyring][img-xfpm-prefs-display]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:100
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Display information on all connected devices][img-xfpm-prefs-devices]\n"
msgstr "![Vis information om alle tilsluttede enheder][img-xfpm-prefs-devices]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:102
#, no-wrap
msgid "When light-locker is available, you can control its settings directly via the power manager.\n"
msgstr "Når light-locker er tilgængelig kan du styre dens indstillinger direkte fra strømstyringen.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:104
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Setup light-locker integration][img-xfpm-prefs-security]\n"
msgstr "![Indstil lys-låser integration][img-xfpm-prefs-security]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour412.md:107
#, no-wrap
msgid "Tab Support"
msgstr "Faneblad-understøttelse"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:110
#, no-wrap
msgid "A long-awaited feature was added: you can now open multiple folders in the same Thunar window.\n"
msgstr "En længeventet facilitet blev tilføjet: du kan nu åbne flere mapper i det samme Thunar-vindue.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:112
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Browse multiple directories][img-thunar-tabs]\n"
msgstr "![Gennemse flere mapper][img-thunar-tabs]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:114
#, no-wrap
msgid "Thunar now displays the remaining free space with a bar in a folder properties.\n"
msgstr "Thunar viser nu den resterende ledige plads med en bjælke i en mappes egenskaber.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:116
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Freespace bar][img-thunar-freespace]\n"
msgstr "![Ledig plads-bjælke][img-thunar-freespace]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:118
#, no-wrap
msgid "And you can select multiple files to see their properties at once.\n"
msgstr "Og du kan vælge flere filer for at se deres egenskaber på én gang.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:120
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Multiple File Properties][img-thunar-multifiles-props]\n"
msgstr "![Flere filegenskaber][img-thunar-multifiles-props]\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour412.md:121
#, no-wrap
msgid "Goodies"
msgstr "Goodies"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:124
#, no-wrap
msgid "There have been lots of improvements to our goodies, and some new and shiny applications have been added by new contributors.\n"
msgstr "Der har været mange forbedringer til vores lækkerier, og nogle nye og skinnende applikationer er blevet tilføjet af nye bidragsydere.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour412.md:125
#, no-wrap
msgid "Alternative panel menu plugin *(xfce4-whiskermenu)*"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:128
#, no-wrap
msgid "The whisker menu is an alternative to the traditional menu plugin, showing favourites, allowing to search through existing apps and much more.\n"
msgstr "Whisker menuen er en alternativ til den traditionelle menu plugin, viser favoritter, tillader at søge gennem eksisterende apps og mere mere.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:130
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Browse through categories][img-whiskermenu-default]\n"
msgstr "![Gennemse kategorier][img-whiskermenu-default]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:132
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Search for an application][img-whiskermenu-search]\n"
msgstr "![Søg efter et program][img-whiskermenu-search]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour412.md:133
#, no-wrap
msgid "Task Manager *(xfce4-taskmanager)*"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:136
#, no-wrap
msgid "The task manager got a revamped user interface, a filter and also supports Gtk3 now.\n"
msgstr "Opgavehåndtering gik en ombygget brugerflade, et filter og understøtter nu også Gtk3.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:138
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Show processes as a tree][img-taskman-tree]\n"
msgstr "![Vis processer som et træ][img-taskman-tree]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:140
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Filter processes by name][img-taskman-filter]\n"
msgstr "![Filtrér processer efter navn][img-taskman-filter]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:144
#, no-wrap
msgid "Parole's UI was totally redone in Gtk3. It now supports multiple video backends, makes more efficient use of your resources and contains a few novel plugins.\n"
msgstr "Parole's UI var totalt genlavet i Gtk3. Det understøtter nu mange video backends, laver mere effektiv brug af dine ressourcer og indeholder nogle få novel plugins.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:146
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Watch videos][img-parole]\n"
msgstr "![Se videoer][img-parole]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:148
#, no-wrap
msgid "The media controls are now contained in a slide-over overlay (with a configurable timeout).\n"
msgstr "Medie-kontrol er nu indeholdt i en glide-over-overlag (med en konfigureret timeout).\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:150
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Listen to music][img-parole-audio]\n"
msgstr "![Lyt til musik][img-parole-audio]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour412.md:151
#, no-wrap
msgid "Text Editor *(mousepad)*"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:154
#, no-wrap
msgid "Mousepad was totally rewritten, gained a settings dialog and now supports Gtk3.\n"
msgstr "Mousepad blev totalt omskrevet, hvorved den fik en indstillingsdialog og understøtter nu Gtk3.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:156
#, no-wrap
msgid "![New mousepad settings][img-mousepad-prefs]\n"
msgstr "![Nye mousepad-indstillinger][img-mousepad-prefs]\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour412.md:157
#, no-wrap
msgid "A note on Xfce's portability"
msgstr "En bemærkning om Xfce's portability"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:160
#, no-wrap
msgid "All but one of those screenshots were taken on machines running OpenBSD -current, a good proof that Xfce is still portable and friendly to all Unix systems.\n"
msgstr "Alle undtagen ét af skærmbillederne blev taget på maskiner der kører OpenBSD -nuværende, et godt bevis på at Xfce stadig er transportabel og venlig på alle Unix-systemer.\n"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: title
#: content/about/tour410.md:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce 4.10 tour"
msgstr "Xfce 4.10 rundvisning"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:8
#, no-wrap
msgid "This tour will introduce you to new major features of Xfce 4.10. It only covers the visual part of what has been done; for the full list of changes, see the [changelogs](/download/changelogs/).\n"
msgstr "Denne rundvisning introducerer dig for nye større funktionaliteter i Xfce 4.10. Den dækker kun de visuelle dele som er lavet; se [ændringsloggene](/download/changelogs/) for en komplet liste med ændringer.\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour410.md:9
#, no-wrap
msgid "Online Documentation"
msgstr "Onlinedokumentation"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:12
#, no-wrap
msgid "During the 4.10 development we've decided to remove user manuals from the packages and move them to an online wiki at [docs.xfce.org](https://docs.xfce.org). The reason for this change is to make [contributing](https://docs.xfce.org/wiki/documentation) and updating the documentation easier.\n"
msgstr "Under 4.10 udviklingen besluttede vi at fjerne brugermanualen fra pakkerne og flytte dem til en online wiki her [docs.xfce.org](https://docs.xfce.org). Grunden for denne ændring er at lave [bidragsydere](https://docs.xfce.org/wiki/documentation) og opdatering af dokumentation nemmere.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:14
#, no-wrap
msgid "![When you click a Help button Xfce will ask you to go to an online wiki page][img-online-help]\n"
msgstr "![Når du klikker en Hjælp knap vil Xfce spørge dig om at gå til en online wiki side][img-online-help]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:16
#, no-wrap
msgid "We hope that with the introduction of the wiki it will be easier for developers and contributors to maintain the documentation.\n"
msgstr "Vi håber at med introduktionen af wiki´en at det vil være nemmere for udviklere og bidragsydere at vedligeholde dokumentationen.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:20
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Collapsed view of the Application Finder][img-appfinder-collapsed]\n"
msgstr "![Sammenfoldet visning af programfinderen][img-appfinder-collapsed]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:22
#, no-wrap
msgid "The application finder has been completely rewritten and combines the functionality of the old appfinder and xfrun4. Apart from user interface improvements, it now allows creating custom actions matching a prefix or a regex pattern.\n"
msgstr "Applikations-finderen er blevet fuldstændig genskrevet og kombinerer funktionaliteten af den ældre appfinder og xfrun4. Bortset fra bruger-grænseflade forbedringer, den tillader ny at skabe brugerdefineret handlinger der matcheren prefix eller et regex mønster.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:24
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Expanded view of the Application Finder][img-appfinder-expanded]\n"
msgstr "![Udviddet visning af programfinderen][img-appfinder-expanded]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour410.md:27
#, no-wrap
msgid "Multiple Rows"
msgstr "Flere rækker"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:30
#, no-wrap
msgid "In 4.10 there is a single panel-wide option for configuring the number of rows in the panel. Some plugins (e.g. *launchers*) fit a single row, while others, like window buttons are allowed to occupy full width of the panel.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:32
#, no-wrap
msgid "![A horizontal panel with a number of rows set to three][img-panel-rows]\n"
msgstr "![Et horisontalt panel med et nummer af rækker sat til tre][img-panel-rows]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour410.md:33
#, no-wrap
msgid "Deskbar Mode"
msgstr "Skrivebordsbjælketilstand"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:36
#, no-wrap
msgid "The panel features a new configuration called a *deskbar* mode. In the deskbar mode the panel is aligned vertically, just like in the vertical mode, but the plugins are laid out horizontally. With multiple rows, it allows creating wide vertical panels suitable for wide-screen setups.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:38
#, no-wrap
msgid "![A panel in Deskbar mode with a number of rows set to five][img-panel-deskbar]\n"
msgstr "![Et panel i skrivebordsbjælketilstand med antal rækker sat til fem][img-panel-deskbar]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour410.md:39
#, no-wrap
msgid "Actions Plugin"
msgstr "Handlinger-plugin"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:42
#, no-wrap
msgid "Session plugin from the xfce4-session package has been merged with a rewritten *actions* plugin\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:44
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Action plugin in a menu mode (left), and in a button mode (right)][img-panel-actions]\n"
msgstr "![Handlinger plugin i en menu-metode (venstre), og in en knappe-metode (højre)][img-panel-actions]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour410.md:45
#, no-wrap
msgid "Window Buttons"
msgstr "Vinduesknapper"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:48
#, no-wrap
msgid "The *window buttons* plugin no longer expands, which makes the plugin positioning more flexible. In order to restore the previous behavior please add a transparent *separator* plugin with the **Expand** option enabled just behind the window buttons plugin.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:52
#, no-wrap
msgid "There are few visual changes in this release of Thunar. The window has less padding and the position of the status bar has been adjusted.\n"
msgstr "Der er få visuelle ændringer in denne udgivelse af Thunar. Vindueet har mindre polstring og positionen af status-baren er blevet justeret.\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour410.md:53 content/about/tour46.md:33
#, no-wrap
msgid "Session Manager *(xfce4-session)*"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:56
#, no-wrap
msgid "The *session manager*'s settings dialog has a button for clearing the saved session (no more `rm -r ~/.config/sessions`). Xfce4-tips has been removed and the session manager can now lock the screen before suspending or hibernating the system.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour410.md:57
#, no-wrap
msgid "Applications Autostart"
msgstr "Automatisk start af programmer"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:60
#, no-wrap
msgid "Another noticeable change is the way GNOME and KDE compatibility works. Compatibility check boxes only enable services, which have to be started before other applications (*gnome-keyring* and *gconf* for GNOME and *kdeinit* for KDE). All other autostart applications are available from **Applications Autostart**, but they are listed using an italic font and not enabled by default in order to distinguish them from Xfce applications. Unlike in previous versions of Xfce, compatibility services can be started independently from each other.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:62
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Applications, which are not a part of Xfce, are listed using an italic font][img-session-autostart]\n"
msgstr "![Applikationer, hvilke ikke er en del af Xfce, er listet ved brug af en italic skrifttype][img-session-autostart]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour410.md:65
#, no-wrap
msgid "Settings Daemon"
msgstr "Indstillingsdæmon"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:68
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce 4.8 used two processes for applying settings: `xfce4-settings-helper` and `xfsettingsd`. In 4.10 they have been merged into xfsettingsd, which now handles all system settings.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:72
#, no-wrap
msgid "The new *settings manager* groups configuration dialogs in categories and allows you to search for their names or descriptions. Most of the dialogs are also now embedded in the settings manager window (this was a compile-time option in Xfce 4.8).\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:74
#, no-wrap
msgid "![The settings manager with icons grouped by category and a search filter applied][img-settings-manager]\n"
msgstr "![Indstillings-manager med ikoner gruppet i kategori og søgnings-filter anvendt][img-settings-manager]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour410.md:75
#, no-wrap
msgid "Settings Editor"
msgstr "Indstillingsredigering"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:78
#, no-wrap
msgid "The *settings editor* no longer collapses the entire tree when you edit a property (this is because it now reloads a single cell rather than the whole tree). Most properties can now be edited in-place, making it easier to quickly adjust settings.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:80
#, no-wrap
msgid "Using settings editor you can also monitor changes of settings in a selected channel. Right-click on a channel in the main window, and select **Monitor** to display the monitor window.\n"
msgstr "Ved brug af indstillings-redigering kan du også tjekke ændringer af indstillinger i en valgt kanal. Højre-klik på en kanal i hoved-vinduet, og vælg **Skærm** for at vise skærm-vinduet.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:82
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Settings editor with an open channel monitor, while editing a property in-place][img-settings-editor]\n"
msgstr "![Indstilling-redigering med en åben kanal viser, imens redigering a ejendom i-pladsen][img-settings-editor]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour410.md:83
#, no-wrap
msgid "MIME Type Editor"
msgstr "MIME-type-redigering"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:86
#, no-wrap
msgid "In the last couple of years, many people were asking for a tool to manage their file type associations. The new *MIME type editor* does just that. It allows you to easily assign a default application to a file type, see your changes and reset them to default settings when necessary. Note that it does not allow you to change the system MIME Type definitions (add or remove types and change icons).\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:88
#, no-wrap
msgid "![MIME types matching a pattern and a menu for selecting a default application][img-settings-mime]\n"
msgstr "![MIME typer matcher et mønster og en menu til at vælge en standard applikation][img-settings-mime]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour410.md:89
#, no-wrap
msgid "Mouse and Touchpad"
msgstr "Mus og pegeplade"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:92
#, no-wrap
msgid "The *mouse and touchpad* dialog is capable of handling basic Synaptics and Wacom properties in the GUI. A settings daemon running in the background handles all kinds of device properties, as documented in the [mouse settings](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfce4-settings/mouse) wiki.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:94
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Synaptics touchpad settings in the mouse and touchpad dialog][img-settings-mouse]\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:98
#, no-wrap
msgid "In 4.10 you can drag and drop a tarball with a downloaded theme onto the *style* or *icon* list. Xfce will attempt to extract and install the files into the `~/.themes` or `~/.icons` directory.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:102
#, no-wrap
msgid "Although the initial plan for Xfce 4.10 was to integrate desktop handling in Thunar, we have decided not to do it at this time yet. Meanwhile, Xfdesktop has gained support for single-click operation, automated background image cycling and thumbnail rendering.\n"
msgstr "Selvom den første plan for Xfce 4.10 var at integrere skrivebords-handlinger ind i Thunar, har vi besluttet ikke at gøre dette denne gang, endnu. Imens, Xfceskrivebordet har fået fremgang for enkelt klik operationen, automatisk baggrunds-billede cykling og miniature rendering.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:104
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Desktop with image thumbnails and support for single-click operation][img-xfdesktop]\n"
msgstr "![Skrivebord med billede miniature og understøttelse for enkelt-klik operation][img-xfdesktop]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:106
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfdesktop is now shipped with a new default background image.\n"
msgstr "Xfskrivebordet er nu udgivet med et nyt standard baggrunds-billede.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:110
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfwm4 can now tile a window when you drag it to the edge of the screen. This feature is optional and is disabled by default. In such a case windows can still be tiled using a keyboard shortcut. Another improvement is a better theming support and cursor key navigation in the tab window (Alt+Tab).\n"
msgstr "Xfwm4 kan nu flise et vindue når du trækker det til kanten af skærmen. Denne funktion er valgfri og er deaktiveret ved standard. I sådan en sag med vinduer, kan stadig flises ved brug af tastaur-genvej. En anden forbedring er et bedre tema support og markør nøgle navigation i tab vinduet (Alt+Tab).\n"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: title
#: content/about/tour48.md:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce 4.8 tour"
msgstr "Xfce 4.8 rundvisning"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:8
#, no-wrap
msgid "This tour will introduce you to all the new major visual features in Xfce 4.8. This is only the visual part of what has been done; for a full list of changes, see the [changelogs](/download/changelogs/).\n"
msgstr "Denne rundvisning introducerer dig for alle de nye større visuelle funktionaliteter i Xfce 4.8. Den dækker kun de visuelle dele som er lavet; se [ændringsloggene](/download/changelogs/) for en komplet liste med ændringer.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour48.md:11
#, no-wrap
msgid "Remote shares browsing"
msgstr "Fjern deler gennemsøger"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:14
#, no-wrap
msgid "Thunar now has optional support for GVFS which will allow you to browse remote shares using Thunar: FTP, Windows Shares, WebDav and SSH servers...\n"
msgstr "Thunar har nu muligheden for understøttelse af GVFS hvilket vil tillade dig at gennemsøge fjern deling ved brug af Thunar: Windows Deling, WebDav og SSH servere ...\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:16
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar browsing a remote share][img-thunar-remote]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar der gennemser en fjern-share][img-thunar-remote]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour48.md:17
#, no-wrap
msgid "New file operations progress dialog"
msgstr "Ny filhandlinger forløb-dialog"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:20
#, no-wrap
msgid "When several file operations (copy or move) are being handled in parallel, Thunar now shows a single progress dialog which displays all the relevant information.\n"
msgstr "Når flere fil operationer (kopiér eller flyt) er blevet håndteret i parallel, Thunar viser nu enkelt fremskridts-dialog hvilket viser alle de relevante informationer.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:22
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Progress dialog][img-thunar-progress]\n"
msgstr "![Forløb-dialog][img-thunar-progress]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour48.md:23
#, no-wrap
msgid "Eject button for removable devices"
msgstr "Skub ud-knap for flytbare enheder"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:26
#, no-wrap
msgid "It is is now possible to eject removable devices by clicking the eject button near each removable device label in the side pane.\n"
msgstr "Det er nu muligt at skubbe aftage enheder ud ved at klikke på skub-ud knappen nær aftagelige enheder mærket i sidepanelet.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:28
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Eject button][img-thunar-eject]\n"
msgstr "![Skub ud-knap][img-thunar-eject]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:32
#, no-wrap
msgid "The Xfce panel has been totally rewritten in 4.8, here are the most visible changes.\n"
msgstr "Xfce panelet er blevet totalt omskrevet i 4.8, her er de mest synlige ændringer.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour48.md:33
#, no-wrap
msgid "Improved positioning and size handling"
msgstr "Forbedret håndtering af placering og størrelse"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:36
#, no-wrap
msgid "The panel has much better support for positioning panels on the screen. It can be dragged and snapped to screen borders; floating positions are only remembered when moving a panel and the length of the panel can be adjusted as a percentage of the monitor size.\n"
msgstr "Panelet har meget bedre understøttelse for positionerings-paneler på skærmen. Det kan trækkes og vrisses til skærmkanter; svævede positionering er kun husket når et panel flyttes og længden af panelet kan justeres som en procentdel af skærmstørrelsen.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour48.md:37
#, no-wrap
msgid "Transparent backgrounds"
msgstr "Transparente baggrunde"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:40
#, no-wrap
msgid "The panel is now able to draw transparent panel backgrounds with non transparent items. Your panel items will remain readable and you will enjoy a nice panel look.\n"
msgstr "Panelet er nu i stand til at tegne gennemsigtige panel baggrunde med ikke-gennemsigtige elementer. Dit panels elementer vil bestå som læsbar og du vil nyde et dejligt panel udseende.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:42
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Transparent panel background][img-panel-transparent]\n"
msgstr "![Transparente panelbaggrund][img-panel-transparent]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour48.md:43
#, no-wrap
msgid "New item editor"
msgstr "Ny element-redigerer"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:46
#, no-wrap
msgid "The panel now features an item editor which allows to modify, move, add and remove items quickly. This is particularly useful for items which are hard to right click and gives you an easy way to change your panel layout from a single place.\n"
msgstr "Panelet har nu den element-funktion redigerer der stillader at modificere, flytte tilføje og fjerne elementer hurtigt. Dette er især nyttigt for elementer der er hårde at højreklikke og giver dig en nem måde at ændre dit panels opsætning fra et enkelt sted.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:48
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Panel item editor][img-panel-editor]\n"
msgstr "![Panel element-redigerer][img-panel-editor]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour48.md:49
#, no-wrap
msgid "Drag and drop to create launchers"
msgstr "Træk og slip for at oprette programstartere"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:52
#, no-wrap
msgid "You can now drag and drop menu entries from the panel applications menu, application finder or Thunar to the panel to create launchers. This feature should please the huge number of people who had been requesting it for ages. The launcher also has an integrated application finder to add new items.\n"
msgstr "Du kan ny trække og sætte menu punkter fra panelets applikations-menu, applikations-viser eller Thunar til panelet for at skabe kørelser. Denne funktion skulle tilfredstille det kæmpe antal af mennesker som har bedt om det i årstal. Kørelsen har også en integreret applikations-finder for at tilføje elementer.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour48.md:53
#, no-wrap
msgid "Window buttons plugin"
msgstr "Vinduesknapper-plugin"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:56
#, no-wrap
msgid "The iconbox and tasklist plugins are new merged into 1 plugin, called window buttons. It implements different sorting modes, improved handling in vertical panels and can draw a similar frame as Xfwm4 Alt+tab when hovering a button.\n"
msgstr "Ikonæsken og opgaveliste plugins er nu sammenlagt ind til 1 plugin, kaldet vindue-knapper. Det implementerer forskellige sorterings-metoder, forbedret handlinger i vandrette paneler og kan tegne en lignende ramme som Xfwm4 Alt+tab når du svæver over en knap.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour48.md:57
#, no-wrap
msgid "New fuzzy clock"
msgstr "Nyt interval ur"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:60
#, no-wrap
msgid "An Xfce release without a new clock mode would not be a true Xfce release. Let us introduce you the 'fuzzy' clock mode!\n"
msgstr "En Xfce udgivelse, uden en ny ur-metode ville ikke være en sand Xfce udgivelse. Lad os introducere dig til 'sløret' ur-måde!\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:62
#, no-wrap
msgid "![New fuzzy clock mode][img-panel-fuzzy-clock]\n"
msgstr "![Nyt interval ur-tilstand][img-panel-fuzzy-clock]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour48.md:63
#, no-wrap
msgid "New directory menu plugin"
msgstr "Nye mappemenu-plugin"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:66
#, no-wrap
msgid "The directory menu plugin provides a menu reproducing the arborescence of a particular folder. This allows you to open a terminal or a file manager in a sub-folder in a very fast and efficient way.\n"
msgstr "Vejviser-menuens plugin tilbyder en menu der genproducerer den træstruktur af en særlig mappe. Dette tillader dig at åbne en terminal eller en fil-bestyrer i en undermapper i en meget hurtigt og effektivt måde.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:68
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Directory menu plugin][img-panel-directorymenu]\n"
msgstr "![Mappemenu-plugin][img-panel-directorymenu]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour48.md:69
#, no-wrap
msgid "Applications menu edition"
msgstr "Applikations-menu udgave"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:72
#, no-wrap
msgid "You can now edit the applications menu using any Freedesktop compliant menu editor, Alacarte being the one we used to test.\n"
msgstr "Du kan nu redigere applikations-menuen ved brug af hvilken som helst Gratis-skrivebord kompliant menu-redigerer a la carte værende den vi brugte til teste.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour48.md:75
#, no-wrap
msgid "Improved multihead setup configuration"
msgstr "Forbedret multihoved indstillings-konfiguration"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:78
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce can now handle and setup multihead setups for any randr 1.2 compatible driver. Unfortunately, this means it will not work with Nvidia proprietary drivers.\n"
msgstr "Xfce kan nu håndtere og sætte multihoved indstillinger for hvilken som helst randr 1.2 kompatibel driver. Desværre, betyder dette at det ikke vil virke med Nvidia's proprietære drivere.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:80
#, no-wrap
msgid "You can enable and disable plugged screens, set their resolution, refresh rate, rotation and reflection, clone screens or extend desktops.\n"
msgstr "Du kan aktivere og deaktivere forbunde skærme, sætte deres opløsning, opdaterings-hastighed, rotation og reflektion, klone skærme eller udvide skriveborde.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:82
#, no-wrap
msgid "![New display settings dialog][img-display-settings]\n"
msgstr "![Ny skærmindstillinger-dialog][img-display-settings]\n"

#. type: Title ####
#: content/about/tour48.md:83
#, no-wrap
msgid "Timed confirmation"
msgstr "Timet bekræftelse"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:86
#, no-wrap
msgid "Any change made with the settings dialog will have to be confirmed within ten seconds or they will be reverted. This prevents broken video drivers from leaving your computer unusable.\n"
msgstr "Enhver ændring lavet med indstillings-dialogen vil blive bekræftet indefor ti sekunder ellers vendt tilbage. Dette undgår ødelagte video drivere fra at forlade din komputer ubrugelig.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:88
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Timed confirmation for display settings changes][img-display-settings-confirmation]\n"
msgstr "![Tidet bekræftelse for skærm-indstillingers ændringer][img-display-settings-confirmation]\n"

#. type: Title ####
#: content/about/tour48.md:89
#, no-wrap
msgid "Quick setup dialog"
msgstr "Hurtig indstillings dialog"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:92
#, no-wrap
msgid "The quick setup dialog allows you to configure a dual screen setup in a second. Plug the second screen, press the display key or Windows + p and select the wanted layout. Done!\n"
msgstr "Den hurtige opsætnings-dialog tillader dig at konfigurere en to-skærms opsætning i ét sekund. Forbind den anden skærm, tryk på skærm tasten eller Windows + p og vælg den ønskede opsætning. Færdig!\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:94
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Quick multihead setup][img-minimal-display-settings]\n"
msgstr "![Hurtig multihoved opsætning][img-minimal-display-settings]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour48.md:95
#, no-wrap
msgid "Settings edition in the Xfce Settings Editor"
msgstr "Indstillings-udgaven i Xfce Indstillings-Redigerer"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:98
#, no-wrap
msgid "The Xfce Settings Editor now deserves its name, it is no longer a simpler Xfconf settings viewer. You can now modify, delete, add and reset settings through its interface. It also monitors changes to update its view.\n"
msgstr "Xfce opsætnings-redigerer fortjener nu dets navn, det er ikke længere en mere simpel Xfconf-indstillingsviser. Du kan nu redigere, slette tilføje og genstarte indstillinger gennem brugergrænsefladen. Det overvåger også ændringer for at opdatere dets udsigt.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:100
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Editing Xfconf properties with the Settings Editor][img-settings-editor]\n"
msgstr "![Redigere Xfconf-egenskaver med indstillingsredigeringen][img-settings-editor]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour48.md:101
#, no-wrap
msgid "Improved keyboard layout selection"
msgstr "Forbedret valg af tastaturlayout"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:104
#, no-wrap
msgid "The layout selection dialog received a lot of love: it no longer displays cryptic language/variants codes but uses localized languages/variants names. Layout edition was also made easier by prefilling the dialogs with the current values.\n"
msgstr "Opsætning selektions-dialogen har modtaget en masse kærlighed: Det viser ikke længere kryptisk sprog/variant-koder men bruger lokaliseret sprog/variant-navne. Opsætnings-udgaven var også gjort nemmere ved at før-fylde dialogerne med de nuværende værdier.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:106
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Layouts and variants list][img-keyboard-settings-list]\n"
msgstr "![Opsætning og variant listen][img-keyboard-settings-list]\n"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: title
#: content/about/tour46.md:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce 4.6 tour"
msgstr "Xfce 4.6 rundvisning"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:8
#, no-wrap
msgid "The long awaited 4.6.0 version of the Xfce Desktop Environment is finally available. We will try to highlight some of the new features which have been added since the last stable release.\n"
msgstr "Den længe ventet version 4.6.0 af Xfce-skrivebordsmiljøet er endelig tilgængeligt. Vi vil prøve at fremhæve nogle af egenskaberne, der er blevet tilføjet siden den sidste stabile udgivelse.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:12
#, no-wrap
msgid "Since desktop icons have been introduced in Xfce 4.4, people have expressed the need to allow the selection of multiple icons (rubber banding). With **Xfce 4.6**, the **Xfdesktop** manager finally implements this feature: you can select multiple icons, remove them, etcetera...\n"
msgstr "Siden skrivebords-ikonerne er blevet introduceret i Xfce 4.4, har folk udtrykt behovet for at tillade en selektion af flere ikoner (gummibånd). Med <b>Xfce 4.6</b>, er <b>Xfskrivebords</b> håndterer endelig implementeret i denne funktion: du kan vælge flere ikoner, fjerne dem og så videre ...\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:14
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Multiple icons selection][img-xfdesktop-rubberbanding]\n"
msgstr "![Valg af flere ikoner][img-xfdesktop-rubberbanding]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:16
#, no-wrap
msgid "**Xfce 4.6** features a brand new desktop menu which allows you to manipulate files as with the **Thunar** filemanager contextual menu, but also to open applications, exit your session, or access the help documentation.\n"
msgstr "<b>Xfce 4.6</b> indeholder et splinternyt skrivebords-menu som tillader dig at manipulere filer som med <b>Thunar</b> filbestyrer kontekst-menu, men også at åbne applikationer, afslutte din session eller få adgang til hjælpe-dokumentation.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:18
#, no-wrap
msgid "![New desktop menu][img-xfdesktop-menu]\n"
msgstr "![Ny skrivebordsmenu][img-xfdesktop-menu]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:22
#, no-wrap
msgid "A lot of long standing bugs have been fixed in **Xfce4 Panel**, particularly for multiple screen setups, but this new release also brings an improved set of panel plugins.\n"
msgstr "Mange af de gamle bugs som er blevet rettet i <b>Xfce4-Panelet</b>, især for flere skærms-opsætning, men denne nye udgivelse bringer også forbedrede sæt af panel plugins.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:24
#, no-wrap
msgid "![New binary clock][img-xfce4-panel-clock]\n"
msgstr "![Nyt binært ur][img-xfce4-panel-clock]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:26
#, no-wrap
msgid "The **clock plugin** has been rewritten to consume fewer system resources and to fix some display bugs, but there is also a new clock mode for the geek in you: binary clock! The new **notification area plugin** allows you to hide selected notification icons to keep your notification area clean and readable.\n"
msgstr "<b>ur plugin</b> er blevet omskrevet til at bruge mindre system ressourcer og rette nogle skærmfejl, men der er også en ny ur-måde for nørden i dig: binært ur! Den nye <b>Underretningsområde-plugin</b> tillader dig at gemme valgte underretningsikoner for at beholde dit underretningsområde rent og læseligt.\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour46.md:27
#, no-wrap
msgid "Sound Mixer *(xfce4-mixer)*"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:30
#, no-wrap
msgid "**Xfce4 Mixer** has been rewritten from scratch to use [Gstreamer](https://gstreamer.freedesktop.org/). This allows us to more easily support multiple sound systems, the user interface is more polished, and you can manage several different sound cards. Additionally, a panel plugin allows you to set the system sound quickly using the mouse scroll wheel.\n"
msgstr "<b>Xfce4 Mikseren</b> er blevet omskrevet fra bund til at bruge [Gstreamer](https://gstreamer.freedesktop.org/). Dette tillader os nemmere at understøtte flere lydsystemer, brugergrænsefladen er mere poleret og du kan håndtere flere forskellige lydkort. Derudover, et panel plugin der tillader dig at sætte systemlyd hurtigt ved brug af musehjulet.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:32
#, no-wrap
msgid "![New sound mixer][img-xfce4-mixer]\n"
msgstr "![Ny lydmikser][img-xfce4-mixer]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:36
#, no-wrap
msgid "**Xfce 4.6** comes with an enhanced session manager: your session should be started faster, and the settings dialog has been reworked to ease the management of session-aware applications. Additionally, the session manager will now automatically restart session applications which crashed so that you are not left without a desktop, panel, window manager, etcetera, if a crash occurs.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:38
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Session settings dialog][img-xfce4-session-settings]\n"
msgstr "![Sessionsindstillinger-dialog][img-xfce4-session-settings]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:40
#, no-wrap
msgid "The session manager also includes a new long-awaited feature: support for **suspend** and **hibernate** \"out of the box.\" The logout dialog now has two additional buttons which offer to suspend or hibernate your computer.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:42
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Session logout dialog][img-xfce4-session-logout]\n"
msgstr "![Sessionsudlogning-dialog][img-xfce4-session-logout]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:46
#, no-wrap
msgid "As usual, **Xfwm4** has matured quite a bit during this release cycle: many bugs have been fixed, support for multiple displays has been added, and overall performance has been improved.\n"
msgstr "Som sædvanligt, <b>Xfwm4</b> er modnet en del under denne udgivelses-cyklus: mange fejl er blevet rettet, understøttelse for flere skærme er blevet tilføjet, og samlet set er ydelsen blevet forbedret.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:48
#, no-wrap
msgid "In addition to some other new features, **Xfwm4** is now able to detect windows that do not respond and offer to terminate them.\n"
msgstr "I addition til nogle andre funktioner, <b>Xfwm4</b> er nu i stand til at registrere vinduer der ikke svarer og tilbyder at lukke dem.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:50
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Dialog to terminate busy applications][img-xfwm4-net-ping]\n"
msgstr "![Dialog til at terminere optagede programmer][img-xfwm4-net-ping]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:52
#, no-wrap
msgid "There is also a new **actions menu** which allows you to quickly move and resize windows, put them above or below other windows, or fullscreen them.\n"
msgstr "Der er også en ny <b>Handlings-menu</b> hvilket tillader dig hurtigt at flytte og tilpasse størrelsen på vinduer, putte dem over eller under vinduer eller fuldskærme dem.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:54
#, no-wrap
msgid "![New actions menu][img-xfwm4-new-menu]\n"
msgstr "![Ny handlingsmenu][img-xfwm4-new-menu]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:56
#, no-wrap
msgid "A new **fill** operation has been implemented; it expands a given window to the available space without overlapping other adjacent windows.\n"
msgstr "En ny <b>fyld</b> operation er blevet implementeret; den udvider en given vindue til tilgængelig plads uden at overlappe andre nærlæggende vinduer.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:58
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Fill operation][img-xfwm4-fill-operation]\n"
msgstr "![Udfyldningshandling][img-xfwm4-fill-operation]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:60
#, no-wrap
msgid "The **compositor** has been optimized to reduce window flickering during resize operations.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:62
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Flicker free resizing][img-xfwm4-resize]\n"
msgstr "![Flimmerfri tilpasning af størrelse][img-xfwm4-resize]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:64
#, no-wrap
msgid "Some **tweakable options** have also been added: for example, you can now disable the blinking of windows when they receive an urgency hint.\n"
msgstr "Nogle <b>tweaksome muligheder</b> er også blevet tilføjet: for eksempel, kan du nu deaktivere vindue-blink når de modtager et tryk fif.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:66
#, no-wrap
msgid "![New tweakable options][img-xfwm4-new-tweaks]\n"
msgstr "![Nye justerbare valgmuligheder][img-xfwm4-new-tweaks]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:70
#, no-wrap
msgid "There have been many bug fixes and performance improvements in **Thunar**. It can use the mouse forward and backward buttons (if available) to navigate, and it includes a new plugin that allows you to set an image as wallpaper from the context menu.\n"
msgstr "Der har været mange fejlretninger og ydelses forbedringer i <b>Thunar</b>. Det kan bruge mus-frem og tilbage knapper (hvis tilgængelig) til at navigere, og det inkluderer en ny plugin der tillader dig at sætte et billede som baggrund, fra kontekst menuen.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:72
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Set an image in a Thunar folder as wallpaper][img-thunar-wallpaper-plugin]\n"
msgstr "![Sæt et billede i en Thunar-mappe som tapet][img-thunar-wallpaper-plugin]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:74
#, no-wrap
msgid "**Thunar** now follows the [XDG user directories](https://freedesktop.org/wiki/Software/xdg-user-dirs) specification; this allows you to have themed and localized user folders to store your music, documents, videos, templates, etcetera...\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:76
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar menu for user directories][img-thunar-xdg-user-dirs]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar-menu til brugermapper][img-thunar-xdg-user-dirs]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:78
#, no-wrap
msgid "**Thunar** will now display a translucent icon for drives or volumes that are not mounted, so that you can distinguish them from the mounted ones.\n"
msgstr "<b>Thunar</b> vil nu vise en gennemsigtig ikon for drev og volumer der ikke er monteret, så du kan skelne dem fra de monterede.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:80
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Translucent icons for unmounted drives and volumes][img-thunar-mounting]\n"
msgstr "![Gennemsigtige ikoner til afmonteret drev og arkiver][img-thunar-mounting]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:82
#, no-wrap
msgid "Last, but not least, **Thunar** now supports encrypted devices!\n"
msgstr "Sidst men ikke mindst, understøtter <b>Thunar</b> nu krypterede enheder!\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:84
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar support for encrypted devices][img-thunar-encrypted]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar-understøttelse af krypterede enheder][img-thunar-encrypted]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:88
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce 4.6 features a new settings interface, **Xfce Settings Manager**, which allows you to configure your desktop environment much more easily than before. The dialogs which are accessible by single clicking on the icons have been designed to be more compact and to allow you to customize your desktop quickly and in a more intuitive way.\n"
msgstr "Xfce 4.6 indeholder en ny indstillings-grænseflade, <b>Xfce indstillings-håndterer</b>, hvilket tillader dig at konfigurere dit skrivebords-miljø meget nemmere end før. Dialogerne hvilket er tilgængelige med et enkelt klik på ikonerne er blevet designet til at være mere kompakte og tillader dig at brugerdefinere dit skrivebord hurtigt og på en mere intuitiv måde.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:90
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Xfce4 Settings Manager][img-xfce4-settings-manager]\n"
msgstr "![Xfce4 indstillingshåndtering][img-xfce4-settings-manager]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour46.md:91
#, no-wrap
msgid "Accessibility settings"
msgstr "Tilgængelighedsindstillinger"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:94
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Accessibility settings dialog][img-xfce4-accessibility-settings]\n"
msgstr "![Tilgængelighedsindstillinger-dialog][img-xfce4-accessibility-settings]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:96
#, no-wrap
msgid "The **Accessibility settings** dialog allows you to set the accessibility related mouse and keyboard options, such as sticky keys, bounce keys, or mouse emulation.\n"
msgstr "<b>Tilgængeligheds-indstillinger</b> dialogen tillader dig at sætte tilgængeligheds-relaterede mus og tastatur indstillinger, såsom klistre taster, springe taster eller mus emulering.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour46.md:97
#, no-wrap
msgid "Appearance settings"
msgstr "Udseendeindstillinger"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:100
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Appearance settings dialog][img-xfce4-appearance-settings]\n"
msgstr "![Udseendeindstillinger-dialog][img-xfce4-appearance-settings]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:102
#, no-wrap
msgid "The **Appearance settings** dialog allows you to set the widget style, the icon theme, and font, toolbar and menu options.\n"
msgstr "<b>Udseende-indstillings</b> dialogen tillader dig at sætte en widget stil, ikon tema og skrifttype, værktøjslinje og menu indstillinger.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour46.md:103
#, no-wrap
msgid "Display settings"
msgstr "Skærmindstillinger"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:106
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Display settings dialog][img-xfce4-display-settings]\n"
msgstr "![Skærmindstillinger-dialog][img-xfce4-display-settings]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:108
#, no-wrap
msgid "The **Display settings** dialog allows you to set the resolution, refresh rate, and the rotation for each screen that is connected.\n"
msgstr "<b>Skærm-indstillings</b> dialogen tillader dig at sætte opløsning, opdaterings-hastighed og rotation for hvert enkel skærm der er forbundet.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour46.md:109
#, no-wrap
msgid "Keyboard settings"
msgstr "Tastaturindstillinger"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:112
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Keyboard settings dialog, layout tab][img-xfce4-keyboard-settings-layout]\n"
msgstr "![Tastaturindstillinger-dialog, layout-faneblad][img-xfce4-keyboard-settings-layout]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:114
#, no-wrap
msgid "The **Keyboard settings** dialog allows you to set keyboard preferences such as key repeating, keyboard shortcuts, and your keyboard layout.\n"
msgstr "<b>Tastatur-indstillinger</b> dialogen tillader dig at sætte tastatur præferencer såsom tast gentagelse, tastatur genveje, og dit tastatur opsætning.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:116
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Keyboard settings dialog, shortcuts tab][img-xfce4-keyboard-settings-shortcuts]\n"
msgstr "![Tastaturindstillinger-dialog, genveje-faneblad][img-xfce4-keyboard-settings-shortcuts]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:118
#, no-wrap
msgid "You can now configure shortcuts more simply, and any shortcut conflicts are automatically detected.\n"
msgstr "Du kan nu konfigurere genveje mere simpelt, og hvilken som helst genvejs-konflikt er automatisk registreret.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour46.md:119
#, no-wrap
msgid "Mouse settings"
msgstr "Museindstillinger"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:122
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Mouse settings dialog][img-xfce4-mouse-settings]\n"
msgstr "![Museindstillinger-dialog][img-xfce4-mouse-settings]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:124
#, no-wrap
msgid "The **Mouse settings** dialog allows you to configure the different mice connected to your computer: button order, acceleration, double-click speed, mouse cursor theme, etcetera...\n"
msgstr "<b>Mus indstillinger</b> dialogen tillader dig at konfigurere forskellige mus forbundet til din komputer: knap orden, acceleration, dobbelt-klik hastighed, mus markør tema og så videre ...\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour46.md:125
#, no-wrap
msgid "Desktop settings"
msgstr "Skrivebordsindstillinger"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:128
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Desktop settings dialog][img-xfdesktop-settings]\n"
msgstr "![Skrivebordsindstillinger-dialog][img-xfdesktop-settings]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:130
#, no-wrap
msgid "The **Desktop settings** dialog is now much more compact; it allows you to configure per-screen settings: wallpaper, brightness, desktop menu, displayed icons, etcetera...\n"
msgstr "<b>Skrivebords-indstillinger</b> dialogen er nu meget mere kompakt; den tillader dig at konfigurere per-skærm indstillinger: baggrundsbilleder, lysstyrke, skrivebords-menu, viste ikoner og så videre ...\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:134
#, no-wrap
msgid "**Xfce 4.6** also comes with a brand new application finder which features a cleaner user interface. It is also easier to use it with the keyboard, and it monitors installed applications to update the list \"on the fly.\" It also allows you to create panel launchers quickly by dragging an application icon to the launcher creation window.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:136
#, no-wrap
msgid "![New application finder][img-xfce4-appfinder]\n"
msgstr "![Ny programfinder][img-xfce4-appfinder]\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour46.md:137 content/about/tour44.md:139
#, no-wrap
msgid "Links"
msgstr "Links"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/tour46.md:141 content/about/tour44.md:143
#, no-wrap
msgid "[Xfce website](https://xfce.org/)\n"
msgstr "[Xfce-websted](https://xfce.org/)\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/tour46.md:141
#, no-wrap
msgid "[Thunar website](https://xfce.org/projects/thunar)\n"
msgstr "[Thunar-websted](https://xfce.org/projects/thunar)\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour46.md:142 content/about/tour44.md:144
#, no-wrap
msgid "Credits"
msgstr "Anerkendelser"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/tour46.md:146
#, no-wrap
msgid "Written by Jérôme Guelfucci (February 2009)\n"
msgstr "Skrevet af Jérôme Guelfucci (februar 2009)\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/tour46.md:146
#, no-wrap
msgid "Screenshots by Jannis Pohlmann\n"
msgstr "Skærmbilleder af Jannis Pohlmann\n"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: title
#: content/about/tour44.md:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce 4.4 tour"
msgstr "Xfce 4.4 rundvisning"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:8
#, no-wrap
msgid "As of today, the long awaited version 4.4.0 of the Xfce Desktop Environment is finally available. I will try to highlight some of the new features which have been added since the last stable release.\n"
msgstr "Fra idag, er den længe ventede version 4.4.0 af Xfce skrivebord-miljøet endelig tilgængelig. Jeg vil prøve at pointere nogle af de nye funktioner som er blevet tilføjet siden den sidste stabile udgivelse.\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour44.md:9
#, no-wrap
msgid "Desktop Icons"
msgstr "Skrivebordsikoner"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:12
#, no-wrap
msgid "One of the most often requested features during the 4.0 and 4.2 was support for icons on the desktop. Now, with Xfce 4.4.0, this feature was finally added to the desktop manager **Xfdesktop**.\n"
msgstr "En af de mest efterspurgte funktioner i løbet af 4.0 og 4.2 var understøttelse af ikoner på skrivebordet. Nu med Xfce 4.4.0, er denne funktion endelig blevet tilføjet til skrivebords-manageren <b>Xfskrivebord</b>.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:14
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Desktop Icons][img-desktop-icons]\n"
msgstr "![Skrivebordsikoner][img-desktop-icons]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:16
#, no-wrap
msgid "The desktop manager utilizes **Thunar**'s libraries to handle application launchers and regular files/folders on the desktop. The desktop manager is also able to display icons for minimized windows on the desktop, which is quite a popular feature from the CDE world. Of course, you can disable the desktop icons altogether if you prefer a clean desktop.\n"
msgstr "Skrivebords-manageren udnytter <b>Thunar</b>'s biblotek til at håndtere applikations-kørelse og almindelige filer/mapper på skrivebordet. Skrivebords-manageren er også i stand til at vise ikoner for minimerede vinduer på skrivebordet, som er en populær funktion fra CDE verdenen. Selvfølgelig, kan du deaktivere skrivebordets ikoner alt-sammen hvis du foretrækker et rent skrivebord.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:18
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Desktop Settings][img-desktop-settings]\n"
msgstr "![Skrivebordsindstillinger][img-desktop-settings]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:20
#, no-wrap
msgid "**Xfdesktop** also continues to provide access to the applications menu, as it did in the previous Xfce releases.\n"
msgstr "<b>Xfskrivebordet</b> fortsætter med at tilbyde adgang til applikations-menuen, som det har gjort i tidligere versioner af Xfce.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:24
#, no-wrap
msgid "The desktop icon support goes hand in hand with the new file manager [Thunar](http://thunar.xfce.org/) which replaces the previous file manager **Xffm**.\n"
msgstr "Skrivebordets ikon understøttelse går i hånd og hånd med den nye fil-manager [Thunar](http://thunar.xfce.org/) som erstatter den tidligere fil-manager <b>Xffm</b>.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:26
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar File Manager][img-thunar]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar-filhåndtering][img-thunar]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:28
#, no-wrap
msgid "**Thunar** was written from scratch to provide an easy to use, but still very lightweight file manager for Xfce. Its user interface was designed to look similar to the file chooser which was introduced with GTK+ 2.4, and other file managers such as **Nautilus** and **pcmanfm** already picked up that idea as well.\n"
msgstr "<b>Thunar</b> var skrevet fra bunden for at tilbyde en nem af bruge, men stadig meget letvægtigt fil-bestyrer for Xfce. Dets brugergrænseflade var designet til at ligne fil-vælgeren som blev introduceret med GTK+ 2.4, og andre fil-bestyrere som <b>Nautilus</b> og <b>pcmanfm</b>havde allerede samlet samme idé op også.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:30
#, no-wrap
msgid "**Thunar** supports all the file management functionality which users will expect, and also several advanced features. For example, a so-called *Bulk Renamer* is included which allows users to rename multiple files at once using a certain criterion.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:32
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar Bulk Rename][img-thunar-bulk-rename]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar masseomdøbning][img-thunar-bulk-rename]\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour44.md:33
#, no-wrap
msgid "Removable Drives and Media"
msgstr "Flytbare drev og medier"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:36
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce 4.4.0 provides easy access to data on removable drives and media. Just insert the media into the drive or plug the new drive in to the computer and an icon representing the removable volume will appear on the desktop and in **Thunar**'s side pane.\n"
msgstr "Xfce 4.4.0 tilbyder nem adgang til data på aftagelige drev og medier. Bare indsæt mediet i drevet eller sæt det nye drev ind i komputeren og et ikon der repræsenterer det aftagelige volume vil dukke frem på skrivebordet og i <b>Thunar</b>'s side panel.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:38
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Removable Volumes][img-removable-volumes]\n"
msgstr "![Flytbare arkiver][img-removable-volumes]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:40
#, no-wrap
msgid "Click on the icon to automatically mount the volume. Right-click the icon to unmount the drive or eject the media from the drive. Note however that this feature requires [HAL](https://freedesktop.org/wiki/Software_2fhal) and is therefore only available for Linux 2.6.x and FreeBSD 6.x and above at the time of this writing (there is limited removable media support for FreeBSD 4.x and 5.x which does not require HAL).\n"
msgstr "Klik på ikonet for automatisk at aktivere volumet. Højre-klik på ikonet for at deaktivere eller skub mediet ud fra drevet. Noter dog at denne funktion kræver [HAL](https://freedesktop.org/wiki/Software_2fhal) og er derfor kun tilgængelig  for Linux 2.6.x og FreeBSD 6.x og over (da dette bliver skrevet) (der er begrænset aftagelige medie understøttelse for FreeBSD 4.x og 5.x hvilket ikke kræver HAL)\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour44.md:41
#, no-wrap
msgid "Text Editor"
msgstr "Tekstredigering"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:44
#, no-wrap
msgid "The new text editor **MousePad** is included with this release. **MousePad** provides all the basic editor functionality, nothing more, nothing less.\n"
msgstr "Den nye tekst-redigerer <b>Muse-Redskab</b>er inkluderet med denne udgivelse. <b>Muse-Redskab</b>tilbyder alle basale redigerings-funktionalitet, intet mere, intet mindre.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:46
#, no-wrap
msgid "![MousePad][img-mousepad]\n"
msgstr "![MousePad][img-mousepad]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:48
#, no-wrap
msgid "You can think of **MousePad** as the equivalent to **NotePad** on Windows. It starts up very fast, usually in less than one second, even on older systems.\n"
msgstr "Du kan tænke at <b>Muse-Redskab</b> er ekvivalent til <b>Notesblok</b> på Windows. Den starter meget hurtigt op, for det meste i mindre end ét sekund, selv på ældre systemer.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:52
#, no-wrap
msgid "**Xfwm4** continues to be the window manager of the hearts.\n"
msgstr "<b>Xfwm4</b> fortsætterne med at være hjerternes vindueshåndtering.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:54
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Xfwm4 ARGB32][img-xfwm4-argb32]\n"
msgstr "![Xfwm4 ARGB32][img-xfwm4-argb32]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:56
#, no-wrap
msgid "This release features an enhanced compositor, supporting transparent ARGB windows, shadows, window frame transparency and much more.\n"
msgstr "Denne udgivelses-funktioner indeholder en forbedret typograf, understøttelse af gennemsigtig ARGB vinduer, skygger, vindue-ramme gennemsigtighed og meget mere.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:58
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Xfwm4 Switcher][img-xfwm4-switcher]\n"
msgstr "![Xfwm4-skifter][img-xfwm4-switcher]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:60
#, no-wrap
msgid "**Xfwm4** also includes a brand new application switcher, as shown in the screenshot above, which displays all windows from the current workspace with icons and window titles.\n"
msgstr "<b>Xfwm4</b> inkluderer også en helt ny applikations-skifter, som vises i skærmbilledet øverst, hvilket viser alle vinduer fra den nuværende arbejdsplads med ikoner og vindue-fliser.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:62
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Xfwm4 Themes][img-xfwm4-themes]\n"
msgstr "![Xfwm4-temaer][img-xfwm4-themes]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:64
#, no-wrap
msgid "Further on support for multiple image formats for window decoration themes was added, including `PNG`, `GIF` and `SVG` images.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:66
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Xfwm4 Tweaks][img-xfwm4-tweaks]\n"
msgstr "![Xfwm4-finjusteringer][img-xfwm4-tweaks]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:68
#, no-wrap
msgid "Advanced controls for the window manager were also added, allowing thorough tweaking of window behavior.\n"
msgstr "Avanceret kontrol for vindue bestyrer var også tilføjet, hvilket tillader grundig tweaking af vindue-opførsel.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:72
#, no-wrap
msgid "The **Xfce4-panel** was completely rewritten for the Xfce 4.4 release. Multiple panels are supported *out of the box* now and can easily be configured using the new **Panel Manager** shown in the screenshot below.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:74
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Panel Manager][img-panel-manager]\n"
msgstr "![Panelhåndtering][img-panel-manager]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:76
#, no-wrap
msgid "One of the major problems in previous Xfce releases was that every plugin had to be run in the same process as the panel, and hence every plugin was able to crash the whole panel. To address this issue, support for external plugins was added to the panel.\n"
msgstr "En af de kæmpe problemer i tidligere Xfce udgivelser var at hvert plugin var nød til at køre i samme process som panelet, og derfor var hvert plugin nød til at krakke hele panelet. For at adressere dette problem, var understøttelse for eksterne plugins blevet tilføjet til panelet.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:78
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Panel Add Item Dialog][img-panel-additem]\n"
msgstr "![Panel Tilføj Punkt Dialog][img-panel-additem]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:80
#, no-wrap
msgid "Developers of panel plugins can now decide whether the plugin should run as external process or as part of the panel process, depending on the stability of the plugin.\n"
msgstr "Udviklere af panel plugins kan nu bestemme om plugin'et burde køre som en ekstern process eller som en del af panel processen, afhængig af stabiliteten, af plugin'et.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:82
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Panel Icon Box Plugin][img-panel-iconbox]\n"
msgstr "![Panelikonboks-plugin][img-panel-iconbox]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:84
#, no-wrap
msgid "Since there is now support for multiple panels, the separate **Xftaskbar4** and **Xfce4-iconbox** utilities are no longer required. Instead, both the taskbar and the iconbox are available as panel plugins now.\n"
msgstr "Siden der nu er understøttelse for flere paneler, er den separate <b>Xfprocesslinje4</b> og <b>Xfce4-ikonæske</b> værktøjer ikke længere påkrævet. I stedet er både processlinhen og ikonæsken tilgængelige som panel plugins nu.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:86
#, no-wrap
msgid "Most of the additional panel plugins, available via the [Xfce Goodies Project](https://goodies.xfce.org/), have been updated for the new panel, and several new plugins were added. For example, the brand new **xfce4-xfapplet-plugin** allows users to add GNOME panel applets to the Xfce panel.\n"
msgstr "De fleste supplerende panel plugins, tilgængelige via [Xfce lækkerier Projektet](https://goodies.xfce.org/), er blevet opdateret til den nye panel, og flere nye plugins er blevet tilføjet. Et eksempel, er den splinternye <b>xfce4-xfapplet-plugin</b> tillader brugere at tilføje GNOME panel applets til Xfce panelet.\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour44.md:87
#, no-wrap
msgid "Time Management"
msgstr "Tidsstyring"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:90
#, no-wrap
msgid "The new time management application **Orage** replaces the **Xfcalendar**, which was introduced with Xfce 4.2.0. **Orage** provides several features to efficiently manage your time.\n"
msgstr "Den nye tidsledelse applikation <b>Orage</b> erstatter <b>Xfkalender</b>, hvilket var introduceret med Xfce 4.2.0. <b>Orage</b> tilbyder flere funktioner til effektivt håndtering af din tid.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:92
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Orage][img-orage]\n"
msgstr "![Orage][img-orage]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:94
#, no-wrap
msgid "While **Orage** is very lightweight and easy to use, it supports all the important features found in larger calendar applications like **Outlook** or **Evolution**. While **Xfcalendar** used the custom `dbh` format in the past to store your settings, **Orage** is based on `ical` and therefore compatible with other calendar applications.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour44.md:95
#, no-wrap
msgid "Terminal Emulator"
msgstr "Terminalemulator"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:98
#, no-wrap
msgid "While **Terminal** was already available during the 4.2 days, it was not mature enough at that time to be part of the core. With this major release, it was moved into the core desktop.\n"
msgstr "Mens <b>Terminal</b> allerede var tilgængelig i løbet af 4.2 dagene, den var ikke moden nok i den tid til at være en del af kernen. Med denne kæmpe udgivelse, var den flyttet ind i kerne-skrivebordet.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:100
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Terminal][img-terminal]\n"
msgstr "![Terminal][img-terminal]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:102
#, no-wrap
msgid "Besides the basic features which you might expect from a terminal emulator, it includes some nice additional features, like multiple tabs per window, customizable toolbars and the ability to configure nearly every aspect of the application via *hidden options*. As can be seen in the screenshot above, this release also supports real transparency using **Xfwm4**'s integrated composition manager.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour44.md:103
#, no-wrap
msgid "Printing"
msgstr "Udskrivning"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:106
#, no-wrap
msgid "**Xfprint**, the Xfce printing management application, saw several small improvements with this release. First, the `a2ps` converter is not mandatory anymore, whilst still recommended. Support for `CUPS` 1.2 was added and **Xfprint** is now able to display the printer state with the `CUPS`-backend.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:108
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Xfce Printing][img-xfprint]\n"
msgstr "![Xfce-udskrivning][img-xfprint]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:110
#, no-wrap
msgid "**Xfprint** also integrates with **MousePad** to provide generic printing support for different kinds of text documents using the `a2ps` converter.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:112
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Xfce Print Dialog][img-xfprint-dialog]\n"
msgstr "![Xfce print-dialog][img-xfprint-dialog]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:114
#, no-wrap
msgid "As you can see the print dialog still looks relatively similar to that of Xfce 4.2, but the internal workings of the printing support were improved, especially the `CUPS` support. Besides that, the printing management functionality was moved to a library, so other applications can use the API to access the printer configuration.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour44.md:115
#, no-wrap
msgid "Autostart"
msgstr "Autostart"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:118
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce 4.4.0 implements the new [Autostart Specification](https://freedesktop.org/wiki/Standards_2fautostart_2dspec) - actually Xfce was the first desktop to implement said feature, but the others were faster to release. ;-)\n"
msgstr "Xfce 4.4.0 implementerer den nye [Autostart Specifikation](https://freedesktop.org/wiki/Standards_2fautostart_2dspec) - faktisk var Xfce det første skrivebord til at implementere den nævne funktion, men de andre var hurtigere til at udgive. ;-)\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:120
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Xfce Autostart Editor][img-autostart]\n"
msgstr "![Xfce-autostartredigering][img-autostart]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:122
#, no-wrap
msgid "The specification consists of two parts, the *Autostart of Applications During Startup*, which is implemented in **xfce4-session** and the *Autostart Of Applications After Mount* which is implemented in [thunar-volman](http://foo-projects.org/~benny/projects/thunar-volman/index.html). This release also includes the **xfce4-autostart-editor**, shown in the screenshot above, which allows users to easily add, remove or disable autostarted applications.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:126
#, no-wrap
msgid "This release introduces new options to customize the desktop to your needs. Some examples of new settings dialogs were already shown in the sections above.\n"
msgstr "Denne udgivelse introducerer nye muligheder til at brugerdefinere skrivebordet til dine behov. Nogle eksempler af de nye indstillings-dialogen var allerede vist i sektionen ovenfor.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:128
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Preferred Applications][img-preferences-applications]\n"
msgstr "![Foretrukne programmer][img-preferences-applications]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:130
#, no-wrap
msgid "The preferred applications framework, which was previously only available in **Terminal**, was imported into Xfce, so users no longer need to edit shell profiles to specify which browser and terminal emulator should be used by Xfce applications. The goal was to make it as easy as possible to change an application for a certain category (GNOME users may have already noticed that GNOME adopted this approach, because it is such simple).\n"
msgstr "Den foretrækkede applikations-rammeværk, hvilket tidligere kun var tilgængelig i <b>Terminal</b>, var importeret ind i Xfce, så brugere ikke længere havde behob for at redigere shell profiler for at specifere hvilken browser og terminal der skulle bruges af Xfce applikationer. Målet var at lave det så nemt som muligt at ændre en applikation for en bestemt kategori (GNOME brugere har muligvis allerede bemærket at GNOME adopterede denne fremgang, fordi det var så simpelt).\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:132
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Keyboard Shortcuts][img-preferences-keyboard]\n"
msgstr "![Tastaturgenveje][img-preferences-keyboard]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:134
#, no-wrap
msgid "And then there was the problem with the keyboard shortcuts in Xfce 4.2... Xfce 4.2 limited the number of freely available keyboard shortcuts, while people wanted to assign any number of keyboard shortcuts. With Xfce 4.4 this limitation is history and the application shortcuts are now separated from the window manager shortcuts.\n"
msgstr "Også var der problemet med tastatur genveje i Xfce 4.2 ... Xfce 4.2 begrænsede nummeret af frit-valgte tilgængelige tastatur-genveje, mens folk ville tildele ethvert nummer af tastatur-genveje. Med Xfce 4.4 var denne begrænsning fortid og applikations-genveje er nu separeret fra vindue-håndterings genveje.\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour44.md:135
#, no-wrap
msgid "Feedback"
msgstr "Feedback"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:138
#, no-wrap
msgid "Please post comments on this article in my [blog](http://xfce-diary.blogspot.com/2007/01/visual-tour-of-xfce-440.html) and use the [xfce](/community/lists) mailinglist if you have questions about Xfce 4.4.0 or trouble with the installation.\n"
msgstr "Venligst, giv kommentarer på artiklen i min [blog](http://xfce-diary.blogspot.com/2007/01/visual-tour-of-xfce-440.html) og brug [xfce](/community/lists) mailing-listen hvis du har spørgsmål omkring Xfce 4.4.0 eller problemer med installationen.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/tour44.md:143
#, no-wrap
msgid "[Thunar website](http://thunar.xfce.org/)\n"
msgstr "[Thunar-websted](http://thunar.xfce.org/)\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:147
#, no-wrap
msgid "Written by Benedikt Meurer, 21 Jan 2007\n"
msgstr "Skrevet af Benedikt Meurer, 21. jan. 2007\n"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: title
#: content/about/news/1734220800.md:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce 4.20 released"
msgstr "Xfce 4.20 er udgivet"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1734220800.md:8
#, no-wrap
msgid "After almost two years of work, we are happy to announce the release of Xfce 4.20 !\n"
msgstr "Efter næsten to års arbejde, er vi glade for at kunne bekendtgøre udgivelsen af Xfce 4.20!\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1734220800.md:12
#, no-wrap
msgid "Since Xfce 4.18 a lot of major development happened. Our team added many nice new features, did a gazillion of bug fixes and did various minor improvements. Finally, all that was released for your pleasure.\n"
msgstr "Siden Xfce 4.18 har der været massere af udvikling. Vores team har tilføjet mange nye fine funktionaliteter, lavede en kæmpe mængde fejlrettelser og diverse mindre forbedringer. Det bliver altsammen langt om længe udgivet til glæde for dig.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1734220800.md:14
#, no-wrap
msgid "<img src=\"//cdn.xfce.org/about/screenshots/4.20-1.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"Xfce 4.20 screenshot\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\"/>\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1734220800.md:16
#, no-wrap
msgid "The major focus during this development cycle was the preparation of the codebase to be ready for Wayland. So that we meanwhile have experimental Wayland support for most components. More details in the links below.\n"
msgstr "Det store fokus i denne udviklingscyklus var forberedelse af kodebasen, så den kan være klar til Wayland. Så vi i mellemtiden har eksperimental understøttelse af Wayland for de fleste komponenter. Der er flere detaljer i linkene nedenfor.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1734220800.md:18
#, no-wrap
msgid "Assuming you have installed Xfce 4.18, here is an overview on the major changes you will see on an upgrade to Xfce 4.20:\n"
msgstr "Hvis vi antager at du har installeret Xfce 4.18, så er her en oversigt over de større ændringer som du vil se ved en opgradering til Xfce 4.20:\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1734220800.md:22
#, no-wrap
msgid "A detailed overview of the changes between Xfce 4.18 and Xfce 4.20 releases can be found on the following page:\n"
msgstr "Et detaljeret overblik over ændringerne mellem Xfce 4.18 og Xfce 4.20 findes på følgende side:\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1734220800.md:26 content/about/news/1671062400.md:26
#: content/about/news/1608595200.md:45 content/about/news/1565568000.md:57
#: content/about/news/1425081600.md:59 content/about/news/1335571200.md:28
#, no-wrap
msgid "This release can be downloaded either as a set of individual packages or as a single fat tarball including all these individual versions:\n"
msgstr "Udgivelsen kan enten downloades som et sæt individuelle pakker eller som en stor tarball med alle de individuelle versioner:\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1734220800.md:29 content/about/news/1671062400.md:29
#: content/about/news/1608595200.md:48 content/about/news/1565568000.md:60
#: content/about/news/1425081600.md:66 content/about/news/1335571200.md:33
#: content/about/news/1295136000.md:39
#, no-wrap
msgid "Best regards,<br />The Xfce development team\n"
msgstr "Med venlig hilsen,<br />Xfce's udviklingshold\n"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: title
#: content/about/news/1671062400.md:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce 4.18 released"
msgstr "Xfce 4.18 er udgivet"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1671062400.md:8
#, no-wrap
msgid "After almost two years of work, we are happy to announce the release of Xfce 4.18 !\n"
msgstr "Efter næsten to års arbejde, er vi glade for at kunne bekendtgøre udgivelsen af Xfce 4.18!\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1671062400.md:12
#, no-wrap
msgid "Since Xfce 4.16 a lot of major development happened. Our team added multiple nice new features, did a gazillion of bug fixes and did various minor improvements. Finally, all that is going to be released for your pleasure.\n"
msgstr "Siden Xfce 4.16 har der været massere af udvikling. Vores team har tilføjet adskillige nye fine funktionaliteter, lavede en kæmpe mængde fejlrettelser og diverse mindre forbedringer. Det bliver altsammen langt om længe udgivet til glæde for dig.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1671062400.md:14
#, no-wrap
msgid "<img src=\"//cdn.xfce.org/about/screenshots/4.18-1.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"Xfce 4.18 screenshot\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\"/>\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1671062400.md:16
#, no-wrap
msgid "This development cycle was influenced a lot by [GSoC 2021](https://summerofcode.withgoogle.com/archive/2021/organizations/5706869816950784) and [GSoC 2022](https://summerofcode.withgoogle.com/programs/2022/organizations/xfce), which led to various new features, most of them for Thunar, the Xfce File Manager. Though as well multiple other Xfce components got a lot of love and many improvements were done under the hood.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1671062400.md:18
#, no-wrap
msgid "Assuming you have installed Xfce 4.16, here is an overview on the major changes you will see on an upgrade to Xfce 4.18:\n"
msgstr "Hvis vi antager at du har installeret Xfce 4.16, så er her en oversigt over de større ændringer som du vil se ved en opgradering til Xfce 4.18:\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1671062400.md:22
#, no-wrap
msgid "A detailed overview of the changes between Xfce 4.16 and Xfce 4.18 releases can be found on the following page:\n"
msgstr "Et detaljeret overblik over ændringerne mellem Xfce 4.16 og Xfce 4.18 findes på følgende side:\n"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: title
#: content/about/news/1608595200.md:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce 4.16 released"
msgstr "Xfce 4.16 er udgivet"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1608595200.md:8
#, no-wrap
msgid "Today, after 1 year and 4 months of work, we are happy to announce the release of the Xfce desktop 4.16, a new stable version that supersedes Xfce 4.14.\n"
msgstr "I dag, efter 1 år og 4 måneders arbejde, er vi glade for at kunne bekendtgøre udgivelsen af Xfce-skrivebordet 4.16, en ny stabil version som afløser Xfce 4.14.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1608595200.md:12
#, no-wrap
msgid "4.16 was a special cycle in many respects (not only pandemic-wise, but also). One of the corner-stones of the non-code changes concerns our migration to GitLab, which is a change in development workflow and a huge step forward in terms of becoming more contributor-friendly and welcoming. In parts, the [humungous changelog of Xfce 4.16](https://www.xfce.org/download/changelogs/4.16) can be attributed to new contributors proposing merge requests (288 merge requests were merged or closed against our core components alone!). We also created a reference Docker container ([xfce/xfce-build](https://hub.docker.com/r/xfce/xfce-build)) and added CI pipelines to all components to ensure we don´t break the build. None of this would have been possible without our hosting being sponsored by [Gandi](https://gandi.net) and [Fosshost](https://fosshost.org)!\n"
msgstr "4.16 was a special cycle in many respects (not only pandemic-wise, but also). One of the corner-stones of the non-code changes concerns our migration to GitLab, which is a change in development workflow and a huge step forward in terms of becoming more contributor-friendly and welcoming. In parts, the [humungous changelog of Xfce 4.16](https://www.xfce.org/download/changelogs/4.16) can be attributed to new contributors proposing merge requests (288 merge requests were merged or closed against our core components alone!). We also created a reference Docker container ([xfce/xfce-build](https://hub.docker.com/r/xfce/xfce-build)) and added CI pipelines to all components to ensure we don´t break the build. None of this would have been possible without our hosting being sponsored by [Gandi](https://gandi.net) and [Fosshost](https://fosshost.org)!\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1608595200.md:14
#, no-wrap
msgid "Another big change concerns our visual identity, which we updated from a strange mix of random (partly Tango-based) icons and not following any naming scheme to a new, visually consistent set (following the freedesktop.org naming specification and a fixed color palette). We´re aware this will generate some work for icon theme maintainers (if they really want to override our gorgeous icons ;)) but we believe the longterm benefit outweighs this one-time effort.\n"
msgstr "Another big change concerns our visual identity, which we updated from a strange mix of random (partly Tango-based) icons and not following any naming scheme to a new, visually consistent set (following the freedesktop.org naming specification and a fixed color palette). We´re aware this will generate some work for icon theme maintainers (if they really want to override our gorgeous icons ;)) but we believe the longterm benefit outweighs this one-time effort.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1608595200.md:16
#, no-wrap
msgid "<img src=\"//cdn.xfce.org/about/tour/4.16/upstream-icons.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"upstream-icons\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\"/>\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1608595200.md:18
#, no-wrap
msgid "And then finally we did some housekeeping (e.g. by dropping Gtk2 support code) and we also added features and improvements - all while sticking to a reasonable release cycle timeframe.\n"
msgstr "And then finally we did some housekeeping (e.g. by dropping Gtk2 support code) and we also added features and improvements - all while sticking to a reasonable release cycle timeframe.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1608595200.md:20
#, no-wrap
msgid "So without further ado, here go the **main highlights of this release**:\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1608595200.md:35
#, no-wrap
msgid "The [window manager](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfwm4/start) received lots of updates and improvements again in the area of compositing and GLX. If a primary display was set, the alt-tab dialog will now only be shown there. Furthermore some handy new options to zoom the cursor along with rest of the display as well as an option to keep minimized windows in the most recently used list complement this release.\n"
msgstr "The [window manager](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfwm4/start) received lots of updates and improvements again in the area of compositing and GLX. If a primary display was set, the alt-tab dialog will now only be shown there. Furthermore some handy new options to zoom the cursor along with rest of the display as well as an option to keep minimized windows in the most recently used list complement this release.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1608595200.md:35
#, no-wrap
msgid "We added a new plugin to the [panel](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfce4-panel/start) dubbed “statustray” which combines both StatusNotifier and legacy Systray items. An animated autohide transition now clearly shows the user “where the panel has gone” and a dark mode (enabled by default) makes the panel drop into the background a bit more with bright themes like the Gtk default Adwaita. Quite a few more smaller improvements were also introduced like accessing desktop actions from a Launcher´s right-click menu, the Window Buttons plugin now offering to `Launch a new instance` of an application and the Workspace Switcher now optionally showing automatic numbering for workspaces.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1608595200.md:35
#, no-wrap
msgid "Support for fractional scaling was added to the [display dialog](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfce4-settings/display), along with highlighting the preferred mode of a display with an asterisk and adding aspect ratios next to resolutions. Falling back to a working mode after misconfiguring the display layout has also been made more robust.\n"
msgstr "Support for fractional scaling was added to the [display dialog](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfce4-settings/display), along with highlighting the preferred mode of a display with an asterisk and adding aspect ratios next to resolutions. Falling back to a working mode after misconfiguring the display layout has also been made more robust.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1608595200.md:35
#, no-wrap
msgid "A new tab in the “About Xfce” dialog shows basic system information like CPU or GPU type. Furthermore the layout and visuals of the dialog were improved.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1608595200.md:35
#, no-wrap
msgid "The [settings manager](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfce4-settings/start) has improved search and filter capabilities. Furthermore all settings dialogs now use window decorations drawn by Gtk (client side decorations).\n"
msgstr "The [settings manager](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfce4-settings/start) has improved search and filter capabilities. Furthermore all settings dialogs now use window decorations drawn by Gtk (client side decorations).\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1608595200.md:35
#, no-wrap
msgid "The “Mime Settings” and “Preferred Applications” dialogs were merged into the “Default Applications” dialog - making it easier for users to set which application handles which filetype or action from one place.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1608595200.md:35
#, no-wrap
msgid "Our file manager [Thunar](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/thunar/start) received a boatload of fixes and quite a few notable features, including pause for copy/move operations, support for queued file transfer, remembering view settings per directory and support for transparency in Gtk themes.\n"
msgstr "Our file manager [Thunar](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/thunar/start) received a boatload of fixes and quite a few notable features, including pause for copy/move operations, support for queued file transfer, remembering view settings per directory and support for transparency in Gtk themes.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1608595200.md:35
#, no-wrap
msgid "Our [thumbnailing service tumbler](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/thunar/tumbler) became more flexible by being able to exclude paths. Furthermore support for .epub (e-book format) was added.\n"
msgstr "Our [thumbnailing service tumbler](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/thunar/tumbler) became more flexible by being able to exclude paths. Furthermore support for .epub (e-book format) was added.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1608595200.md:35
#, no-wrap
msgid "The [session manager](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfce4-session/start) offers improved support for GPG agent 2.1 and the setting dialog was visually improved.\n"
msgstr "The [session manager](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfce4-session/start) offers improved support for GPG agent 2.1 and the setting dialog was visually improved.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1608595200.md:35
#, no-wrap
msgid "The [power manager](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfce4-power-manager/start) received a lot of bugfixes and some smaller features - among them a cleanup of its settings dialog, an optional visual indicator for when `Presentation Mode` is enabled, more accurate battery status icons and automatically dismissing low-power notifications upon the connection of a charger.\n"
msgstr "The [power manager](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfce4-power-manager/start) received a lot of bugfixes and some smaller features - among them a cleanup of its settings dialog, an optional visual indicator for when `Presentation Mode` is enabled, more accurate battery status icons and automatically dismissing low-power notifications upon the connection of a charger.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1608595200.md:35
#, no-wrap
msgid "The [desktop](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfdesktop/start) mostly received bugfixes and small improvements - and the new default wallpaper!\n"
msgstr "The [desktop](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfdesktop/start) mostly received bugfixes and small improvements - and the new default wallpaper!\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1608595200.md:35
#, no-wrap
msgid "Our menu library [garcon](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/garcon/start) received new APIs and now doesn´t launch applications as children of the process hosting the menu anymore. The previous behavior led to applications crashing along with e.g. the panel.\n"
msgstr "Our menu library [garcon](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/garcon/start) received new APIs and now doesn´t launch applications as children of the process hosting the menu anymore. The previous behavior led to applications crashing along with e.g. the panel.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1608595200.md:35
#, no-wrap
msgid "The [applicaton finder](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfce4-appfinder/start) now allows for sorting applications by “frecency” - a combination of frequency and recency.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1608595200.md:35
#, no-wrap
